Nawudu ro futu kuli kwasabe koronabairos (COVID-19) dǝ European Union/European Economic Area-a United Kingdom-a, lan tǝrain dǝ tǝn 1 January sǝta 15 March 2020 ro isǝna dǝ
Futu kuli kwasabe coronvirus (COVID-19) dǝ waatǝ nzǝ dǝ jili tilo fǝlejin European Union/lardǝwa European ye kasuwunzǝ sǝdin-a United Kingdom-a dǝ ye tawatsǝna kǝla, nangam wo son lǝatar lardǝ dǝ ye ro, kwasa COVID-19 ye dǝ naudu ro tǝrain lardǝwi yo son.
Futu Italy, lardǝwa, litariwa-a naa kam zauro dondi rotǝye son turuna dǝyeyi dawari nza sasara kǝla am kwasa COVID-19 ye zamzǝna dǝ nguwujin yen sandi dǝwo ne nǝlefa ro cistuwu tanas ma ro cistuwu kam zauro dondi ye mǝradzain yen.
Yim 31 December 2019 lan, jami la kwasa nimoniya ye zamzǝna ma dǝwo futu gotin ma dǝ kǝlanzǝ notǝnyi ma ye hawar tuwondǝna suro bǝla Wuhan ye, sidi Hubei ye lardǝ China ye dǝ lan.
Yim 9 January 2020 lan, cidaram kwasa kaltǝye lardǝ China ye dǝ ye hawar awo kwasa dǝga suwudin ye cina kǝla shima kwasa bǝlin dǝwo koronabairos lan buwotin ma dǝ dǝ gullono kuru sha kwasa yintǝ dabtǝgǝ ye sha koronabairos 2 (SARS-COV-2) lan notǝna dǝ wono.
Tǝn loktu adǝn, kǝndondi dǝwo SARS-CoV-2 men wazuna wo so kwasa coronavirus yen buwotin (COVID-19).
Kuwo so ro awo shadatǝna dǝ shima kashi 80% am dǝwo COVID-19 kwasa kambayi la sandi lan mbeji, i.e kwasa yintǝ ye nimoniya aw ba ma, kuru nguwunza so ngazana.
ca lan kashi 14% kwasa COVID-19 ye so, kwasa kǝraw ro lezǝ waljin shi dǝwo ne litarin buna mǝradǝzǝna ma kuru kashi 6% gabsǝna dǝ kwasa kǝraw ye sandiya zamjin shi dǝwo ne zauro cistuwu mǝradǝzǝna ma.
Batǝ dǝwo am COVID-19 ye litarin bozǝgǝna dǝ ye dǝ kashi ca 4%.
Suro nazarǝ adǝ yen, ande ye futu watǝ COVID-19ye dǝ kulasnyen suro lardǝwa European Union/lardǝwa European Union ye kasuwu sǝdin (EU/EEA) kuru United Kingdom (UK)-a yen sha Hubei lardǝ China ye dǝga ratalnye ruyen.
Ande ye kuru man nǝm nguwu am kwasa COVID-19 ye suro lardǝ EU/EEA-a UK-a kǝrma ye dǝga lardǝ Italy ye dǝga ratalnye ruyen suro yim 31 January -15 March 2020 suwudǝnan.
Kwasa COVID-19 suro lardǝwa EU/EEA-a UK-a yen
Ngawo China yen, kwasa COVID-19 ye dǝ tartǝyina kara lardǝwa dinaben kuru futu COVID-19 ye dǝ dina gabsǝna dǝn lejin dǝ futu lardǝ tudu yeyi ro lejin.
Yim 11 March 2020 yen, Cidama kura karabka Nǝlefa ye Dinaye ma dǝ ye shi kwasa COVID-19 dǝ kwasa dina samma so ye ro wurmawono.
Yim 5 March lan lamar Eurosurveilance 2020, Spiteri etal. hawar kǝn hawal me COVID-19 ye cina futu WHO ye bayanzǝna ye dǝ yeyi.
Suro EU/EEA yen, am kwasa dǝ zamzǝna tawatkata sandi yakkǝ dǝ lardǝ France ye mauzǝ yim 24 January 2020 lan suro am dǝwo Wuhan, sidi Hubei ye lardǝ China yen isana so dǝ yen.
Yim 15 March 2020 lan, am kwasa COVID-19 ye zamzǝna so dǝ suro lardǝwa 30 EU/EEA-a United Kingdom (UK)-a ye samma son tuwondǝna, kuruman kate kate 31 December 2020-a kuru kawu kuntawu ye shima dǝn kunten, am kwasa dǝ ye zamzǝna 39,768-a am 1,727 bazana-a hawar tina, kuru am kwasa dǝ zamzǝna 17,750-a am 1, 441 bazana suro Italy ye runzǝ man.
Futu adadu jumla am kwasa COVID-19 ye zamzǝna ye fando
Na dawudi kwasa ro cistuwu ye Europ ye (ECDC) dǝ, hawar am kwasa COVID-19 ye zamzǝna lardǝwi yo so ye isabtin dina samma son, fantǝram maila yen tuwondǝna men alama lardǝ dǝ ye cidaramnzǝ nǝlefa ye so yeyi, wumawa nǝlefa ro cistuwu ye lardǝ ye so, WHO, soro hawar sadin wajiya son sa 8:00 a.m.
Katabwa adǝn faidatǝ letǝ COVID-19 ye dǝ suro EU/ EEA-a UK-a ye dǝ ngaltin kuru sha Italy ye dǝga rataltǝyin.
Alama tartǝ kwasa COVID-19 ye dǝ wakiltǝ yeyin, nde ye jumla am kwasa COVID-19 dǝ ye zamzǝna ye kawu-14 ye komnyiye, adǝyeyi men futu kwasa COVID-19 ye dǝ Alayi men gotin dǝ ye ro hangal gǝnayena, suro lardǝwa. EU/EEA-a UK-a wo son, yim 1 January-15 March 2020 ro isǝna yen.
Adǝyeyi ma ande ye jumla adadu am kwasa dǝ ye zamzǝna ye nowata ma lardǝwi so hayena yim 15 March 2020 8:00 a.m sandiya Italy dǝga rataljiye 31 January-15 March 2020 ro suwudǝnan dǝga.
Letǝram COVID-19 ye suro lardǝwa EU/EEA- UK-a dǝ ye
Letǝram COVID-19 ye kasarrata ma kawu-14 ye ma suro EU/EEA-a UK-a ye dǝ nguwu so jili Hubei (China)ye dǝ zasaa (Sura1).
EU/EEA-a UK-a samma son, jumla COVID-19 watǝ COVID-19ye ye dǝ yim 21 February ga tǝra badiwono kuru gana waltǝ kara 28 February 2020ye dǝn tǝrana (Hujjawa duno cin ma).
Adǝ nguwu so adadu dǝwo am kwasa dǝ ye zamzǝna ye lardǝ Italy ye futu nagaduro tǝrain dǝ hawaratǝna lan tuwongatǝ, amma lardǝwa gade EU/EEA-a UK-a so dǝ letǝram futu COVID-19 ye tǝrain dǝ jili tilo fǝlezǝ (Hujjawa duno cin ma).
Taswira 2 dǝ fǝlejin adadu jumla am COVID-19 zamzǝna suro lardǝwa EU/EEA-a UK-a ye dǝ fǝlejin, kuru futu sha Italy ye dǝga rataltǝna dǝ yim 31 January-15 March 2020 ye ma dǝ.
Shi dǝ fǝlezǝna kǝla, yim 15 March 8:00 a.m, lan lardǝwa gade EU/EEA-a UK-a so ye hawar buroza sadǝna kǝla jumla am kwasa dǝ ye zamzǝna ye ma dǝwo Italy ye ma dǝro ratallata ma dǝ mawu ǝ kawu dǝwo ro aw shin cidaan.
Kulashinde ye fǝlezǝna kǝla adadu am dǝwo kwasa dǝ ye zamzǝna ma nowata ma so dǝ nagaduro tǝrain suro EU/EEA-a kuru UK-a ye dǝn.
Futu letǝram suro jumla wawa COVID-19 ye dǝro hangal gǝnatǝna dǝ ye fǝlezǝna, kwasa dinaram adǝ nagaduro tǝrain jili tilo ro lardǝwa samma son.
Adǝ ye lardǝwa samma hal dasana dǝ gade gade son yayi, nǝm gade nǝlefa jamaye ro cistuwu ye, kuru waneye dǝlǝu kam kwasa COVID-19 ye sǝtana ngaltǝye, kuru man dǝlǝu kam kwasa COVID-19 ye sǝtana ngaltǝye, ngaltǝ am dareye so-a kunten.
Badiyaram kuntawu March 2020 ye, litawa naa zamtǝna suro Italy ye dǝ ye bayanzǝna kǝla ca 10% dǝwo COVID-19 ye zamzǝna so dǝ zauro cistuwu mǝradǝzǝna kuru fatowa hawar ye so gulzana kǝla litariwa so-a ba zauro am ro cistuwu ye so-a ba kek sǝmbuluwuna wada.
Katabwa kǝla am COVID-19 ye sǝtana so litarin kuru/aw naa am ro zauro cistuwu ye so ba EU /EEA-a yen tuwondin 6%-a 1%-a jong yin ndaso wo so (katab dǝ fǝletǝnyi).
Kuru adǝyeyi ma, sandiya kǝla fasal yen sabtǝ, bayan sabtǝ am zamtǝna ye kǝrmaro tǝdin dǝga banatǝ ro shi dǝwo ne kǝla am zamtǝna-a am bazana-a ro hangal cina ma dǝ.
Nazarǝ la 2010-11 lan tǝdǝna dǝ ye zauro naa zauro am ro cistuwu dǝ-a baa am daudau ro cistuwu ye dl-a lan zauro faltǝna ro fǝlezǝna suro Europe ye dǝn, 29.2 lan tai Germanye lan diyelwa 4.2 tǝadir jama 100,000 wo son suro Portugal yen.
Adǝbe fǝlezǝna lardǝwa do waneye Italy ga razǝwu nozain aw satinmba ( diyelwa 12.5 naa zauro am ro cistuwu ye-a naa am ro cistuwu dawu dawu ye-a tǝadir jama 100,000 suro 2010-11).
Halla la nǝm kura nǝlefa ro cistuwu ye tandǝm tulo, lardǝwa EU/EEA-a UK-a so ro tǝadirrata kǝla am COVID-19 zamzǝ litarin rotǝna dǝ ye >90% so diyelwa naa zauro am ro cistuwu ye dǝga nǝm nguwun kozain yen, bayanzǝna suro kulashi duwaye kǝla tajirwa COVID-19 ye ECDC ye dǝn.
Am zamtǝna so dǝ suro lardǝwa EU/EEA-a UK-a ye dǝn nǝm nguwunza zauro na kozuna dǝga, kuru litari so-a naa zauro am ro cistuwu ye so dǝ naa kureyata musamman ro cidayin mbeji dǝga, hawar kǝla am zamtǝna so ye dǝ-a diyelwa naa zauro am cistuwuye dǝga ca mbeji ma ngǝlawo na su ndaraye so tǝkin dǝn yisawu 2 (NUTS-2) nankaro.
Futu Italy lan turuna dǝyeyi kuru futu letǝram lardǝwa gade son kǝrmaro wajin dǝ ye fǝlezǝna kǝla kwasa dinaram ye COVID-19 dǝ nagaduro tǝrain suro EU/EEA-a UK-a ye dǝn.
Lardǝwa, litariwa-a naa zauro am ro cistuwu ye-a adǝ nankadǝro kǝlanza dawarza kǝla dawari ba kǝla klalan suro jama yen SARS-COV-2 tartǝyina yen kuru adadu am COVID-19 ye zamzǝna dǝ tǝrain yen sandi dǝwo ne nǝlefa ro cistuwu mǝradǝzǝna yen, kuru tanas maro zauro cistuwu, futu jili naa dǝwo zamtǝna Italy ye dǝ yeyi.
Futu suro ECDC ye kulashi nzǝ duwa duwabe kǝla tajirwa ye karǝngǝ ye dǝn fǝlezǝna dǝ yeyi, fasal la duwa duwaye, datelaye, kuru kǝzǝbkǝ ma dǝ zauro faida SARS-COV-2 dǝ tartǝgǝ nzǝ dǝga wahartǝge ro, cistuwu lan citǝ fasal kaltǝgǝye ro gǝrta ro, futu adadu am zamtǝna ye duwa duwa ro tǝrain ro tǝmatǝna dǝ ye waneye muwonzǝ shawari kamtǝma so-a litari so-a ro loktu kǝzǝbkǝ cǝ lamar dǝga ngǝlaro asuzainmba, samoyinmba, kuru nanza so dǝga kalkalzayinmba date lan cidatǝ baditǝnyi ma.
Kulashi duwa duwa ye kǝla tajirwa ye dǝ kuru man katabwa nǝlefa jamaye dǝye isabsǝ suwudin kaziyi kwasa dinaram ye dǝga kambaitǝgǝ ro.
Dǝlǝu la loktu gana ye mbeji loktu shima dǝn lardǝwa so muwonzǝ kasadǝnza SARS-COV-2 tǝ tartǝ nzǝ dǝ waharzayin kuru kǝrau kǝla nǝlefa ro cistuwu ye dǝga fuluzain.
Adǝ dewo ro teriya, tǝmatà fasalla nǝlefa ro cistuwu ye lardǝwa EU/EEA-a ye dǝ am dondi dǝwo zauro cistuwu mǝradǝzǝna kada rurutayin ro suro kaw gana aw mawwa ishin dǝ yen.
Fǝlangtǝ kwasa coronavirus (COVID-19) ye dǝ, shi dǝwo ne kwasa yintǝ dabtǝgǝ ye dǝwo (SARS) Koronabairos 2 (SARS-COV-2) ye suwudǝnan dǝ, ba burozǝ kǝrmaro am 3000 kǝn samin yeyi cezǝna kuru am 80,000 zamzǝna suro lardǝ China ye-a naa gade suro dina yen-a son, sǝkǝ tajirwa kura adam gana ro suwudǝnan.
Futu kuli kwasabe shiga samǝn ma dǝ yeyi, SARS-COV, shi dǝwo ne am duwu kada ro SARS suwudǝnan dǝ suro saa 2003, shi SARS-COV-2 dǝ ye waneye batata men gotin kuru alamawa kǝndondibe jili tilowa ma fǝlejin fasal jili tilowa men.
Son yayi, COVID-19 dǝ nǝm zau-a tajirwa-a lan SARS ye dǝyeyi sǝtǝnyi amma shi dǝ zauro tartǝyina kuru shi dǝ am ngǝlinza lezǝna ma zauro sǝtain wo zairowa yayiro kuru kongawa ma nguwu ro sǝtain wo kamuwa yayiro.
Futu nagaduro kitawwa kǝla futu kwasa dǝ falangjin dǝ yen lǝbtǝ tǝrain dǝ yen, ruwo adǝ ye bayanna suro loktu yen duwa duwa ro cin kǝla mauduwa kulashi ilmu yen.
Ande ye suro dǝn awowa buro hawal yin notiya sandǝna so kǝrenyen kǝla nazaru ilmuye kǝla futu kwasa tartǝyin-a kaltǝyin-a ye-a, nazaru ilmuye kǝla futu garram aw fǝrtǝ kwasabe-a, nazaru ilmuye kǝla kuli kwasabe, kulashi kǝla alamawa kǝndondiben, kurun diwo, shawari liyitaye kǝnjo, kwasa dǝn yitkawo-a
Korowa kada jawaw mǝradǝzana son yayi, tǝmanyena bayan adǝ ye banazǝ kwasawa tajirwa dǝga asutin kuru kǝriwu tin.
Kawuske bikaye January 25 2020 be dǝ, awo dǝwo tǝmatǝnyi kuru awo dǝwo ngaltema njastinmba ye ro walzǝna am lardǝ China ye samma so ro dǝwo sandiya sakǝ faton zakta namzana so loktu batalla shima dǝyen kuru mawwa kada ro ngawo shima dǝyen sawo falangtǝ kwasa la kǝla notǝnyi yen.
Kuli kwasabe dǝ zaumaro coronavirus (CoV) dǝwo kwasa yintǝ ye (SARS) 2003; dǝ suwudǝnan dǝga samǝn adǝ sǝkǝ, karabka Nǝlefa ye Dinaye (WHO) sha SARS-COV-2 lan buwono yim February 11, 2020, kuru kwasa dǝwo shi men tuwondin dǝ kwasa-19 CoV yen buwotǝ (COVID-19).
Kwasa dinan fomjin adǝ bǝla Wuhan, China, kuru duwa duwa ro lardǝ samma so ro tarratǝgǝ kuru lardǝwa 50 yeyi ro kǝla dina yen tarratǝgǝ.
