Fǝrtǝ dǝ-a gǝnatǝna nzǝ dawu dawu ye-a
Notǝna ye dǝ yeyi SARS-CoV dǝ-a MERS-Cov dǝ-a so fǝrtǝnza batata men ciwono kuru am so ro ngam-a kalimo-a men tarratǝgǝ.
Fasal nzudu rataltǝye dǝwo phylogenetic comparison of SARS-CoV-2 dǝ men rokko CoVs gade so dǝ-a, batata so dǝ sandima ngawar SARS-CoV-2 ye wo ro gotǝna dalil dǝ kuli kwasabe bǝlin dǝ 96% ro SARS-like CoVs dǝga samǝn wo batata la sha bat-SL-CoVZX45 dǝ-a kuru bat-SL-CoVZX21 dǝ-a lan buwotin dǝ lan.
Ade yeyi ma, gǝnatǝna dawu dawu yé ndaso kuli kwasabe dǝga banaze awo kam so tartǝgǝ dǝga fanjin ma dǝga farzǝ kozǝ ma ro notǝnyi, zawal zǝga tartǝgǝna dǝ ye kwamison asutǝnyi.
Ji, et al., ye kurunzǝ dǝn kadi shima kuli kwasabe dǝga batata lan gozǝ kam so ro tarjiwo shi dǝwo ne S protein na jili tilo ro kǝltana.
Nazaru ilmuye lan, kulashiwu so Guangzhou, China lan, dabba la pangolins - kuruwu-sungullata, cidacida-kǝmbuma nguwu so ro sha kurun kǝska ye China yen faidatain ma- sandima gǝnatǝna SARS-CoV-2 dawu dawu ye ro waljin wada futu 99% ro CoV dǝwo pangolins-a SARS-CoV-2 lan tuwondǝna dǝga samǝn dǝ.
