SARS-CoV-2 dǝ waneye siffa jili tilo wa ro waljin.
Rifot tina kǝla SARS-CoV-2 shi dǝ nur shiro ultraviolet sayin dǝga wazǝna kuru kawudo 50 °C minti 30 ro ; ndin fal, 75% ethanol, chlorine-kurun kuli yazo ye-a kǝllatǝ ma, peracetic acid, chloroform, kuru awowa sha fatty solvents lan buwotin dǝ-a, amma chlorhexidine gǝnyi ma, raksǝ ngǝlaro kuli kwasabe dǝga cejin.
Adamngana so samma so tiyinza dǝ raksǝ SARS-CoV-2 dǝga kǝriwjinmba adǝ nankaro tiinyi kuli kwasabe bǝlin dǝ ye sha sǝtain.
Kǝrma dǝro, Rifot nazaru la kǝzǝbkǝ ye kǝla futu tiyi kamma ye SARS-CoV-2 dǝga kǝriwjin ye ba.
