Nguwu so ro, ngawo kuli kwasabe dǝ tiyi kamma zamjiya, buro salak lan kam dǝye tiyinzǝn alaunzǝ kwasa kǝriwtǝye dǝ asujin zawal asutǝramnzǝ dǝwo sha (PRRs) lan buwotin dǝ men, C-type lectin-like receptors Toll-like receptor (TLR), NOD-like receptor (NLR), kuru RIG-I-like receptor (RLR).
Diwalla kada men, kuli kwasabe sǝkǝ futǝ suwudin, wuratǝ dendritic cells, kuru synthesis type I ye-a interferons (IFNs) shi dǝwo ne kuli kwasabe tartǝgǝ dǝga fulujin kuru sǝrayin macrophage phagocytosis of viral antigens dǝga.
Ade yeyi ma, N protein SARS-CoV ye dǝ raksǝ kuli kwasabe dǝga banaze balimi kwasa kǝriwtǝye tiyi ye dǝn soshin.
Karǝngǝn, balimi kwasa kǝriwtǝye tiyi dǝ ye kuli kwasabe kǝriwtǝ dǝ ro kǝltǝyin.
T lymphocytes rokkozǝn CD4+ kuru CD8+ T cells dǝ taidaza faitǝ dǝn banazain.
CD4+ T cells dǝ B cells dǝga kulleccin balimiwa kwasa kǝriwtǝye dǝ tulo ro, kuru CD8+ T cells dǝ kuli kwasabe dǝga kǝla tilowa ro cejin.
T helper cells dǝ proinflammatory cytokines sutuluyin cells faijin ma dǝga banatǝ ro.
Adǝyeyi ma, CoV dǝ raksǝ cida T cell ye dǝro takkal suwudin shi apoptosis T cells dǝga gǝrǝbtǝgǝ men.
Balimi kwasa kǝriwtǝye tiyi humoral dǝ banama alama C3a dǝ-a kuru C5a dǝ- a kuru balimi kwasa kǝriwtǝye tiyi so-a so zauro faida kuli kwasabe kǝriwtǝ dǝ ro.
Misallo, balimiwa kwasa kǝriwtǝye tiyi dǝwo tiyi kam ngazǝna yen tutuluwuna dǝ MERS-CoV dǝga cezǝna.
Hal gadǝn, fasal balimi kwasa kǝriwtǝye tiyi ye dǝ ye naa kuzǝna ro cidajiya awo la shiro free radicals gultin dega surayin nguwu ro sutuluyin shi dǝwo ne lezǝ fufu-a kǝndǝwu gade so-a, kuru sa bannatiya kǝndǝwu kada cidazainmba ro waljin kuru kǝrmu yayi ro surutsǝyin.
