Hawar jili tilowa ma nazaru la ndi karǝngǝn kǝla yalla zamtǝna-a yalla dǝwo alamawa kǝndondibe fǝlezainmba yen tǝdǝna ye fǝlezǝna.
Rataltǝgǝ men, nazaru la kǝla jama yen suro 2012 yen tǝdǝna dǝ ye fǝlezǝna kǝla am MERS-CoV ye sǝtana dǝ ye kangeya (98%), nzasǝra ngamdu (47%), kuru yintǝ kǝraw (55%) shima alamawa kǝndondibe nza wo.
Adǝyeyi ma, kashi 80% wo so bana yintǝram ye mǝradǝzana, COVID-19 ye sǝtana dǝga kozǝna ro kuru MERS ye loru dǝ COVID-19 ye dǝga kuzǝna.
Shidada (26%) kuru dawu lilimta (21%) ye am MERS ye sǝtana dǝn turuna.
