Coronavirus (CoVs) dǝ yalla Coronavirdae ye dǝn kara, shi dǝwo ne suro nzǝ dǝn samno kǝkǝrrata, positive-sensed, single-stranded RNA viruses mbeji ma.
Kuliwa kwasabe dǝ alowa kura dǝ-a derijin 26 to 32 kilobases suro kuliwa kwasabe RNA ye dǝ sha “CoVs” lan buwotin s siffanzǝ dǝ electron microscope lan wutiya zawa maiye dǝga samǝn dǝro.
Siffa men wunǝmiya, CoVs dǝ alowa yayak tǝnyi fasal gili tilowa ma.
Tǝadirro kashi ndi suro yakkǝ yen alowabe dǝ ye dǝ suro nzan ndi kura kura mbeji (ORF1a and ORF1b), sandiya pp1a kuru pp1ab replicase polyproteins ro fasarrata ma.
Sandi polyproteins so dǝ protiens miyaun arakkǝn ayimaro kǝltǝnyidǝa fuwulan gartǝro sandiya cedo, kwamison sha generate 16 non-structural proteins, sha nsp1~16 lan notǝnama.
Na gade genome ye gabsǝna dǝ suro nzǝn ORFs mbeji structural proteins ye, including spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) and nucleoprotein (N).
Durra-nowata proteins ro kǝllata-a kada sandiye kuruman kǝltana durra CoVs gade gadero.
Nǝm gade gade Proteins ye lǝatar ro, CoVs so dǝ kashi diyau ro yakkatǝ (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV and delta-CoV), suro dǝn beta-CoV genera dǝ suro nzǝn HCoVs nguwu so mbeji kuru shi dǝ diyau ro yakkatǝ (A, B, C and D).
Dalilwa Phylogenetic ye fǝlezǝna kǝla batata-a jilwa so-a dǝ sandima fǝrtǝ alpha-CoVs-a beta-CoVs-a ye wo ro, kuru ngudowa dǝ sandima gamma-CoVs-a delta-CoVs-a dǝ kǝndǝm gotǝna wo.
Saa duwu kada ro, CoVs so dǝ garza alau kada kozana kuru lanza dǝ isa kwasa kura adamngana ye ro wallada.
Ku ro kuden, CoVs (HCoVs) tulur adamgana-a kǝlata notǝ.
Suro nzan HCoV-229E-a HCoV-NL63-a dǝ sandi alpha-CoVs.
Beta-CoVs uwu gade dǝ sandima HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus (SARS-CoV), Middle East respiratory syndrome coronavirus (MERS-CoV) kuru SARS-CoV-2-a.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 kuru HCoV-NL63-a dǝ nguwu so ro alamawa kǝndondibe gana fǝlezain alama tantayi/aw shidada yeyi.
Rataltǝgǝ men, SARS-CoV-a MERS-CoV-a kuru bǝlin ro asutuna ma SARS-CoV-2 dǝ sandi zauro kwasa saudin, kwasa yintǝram ye zau ma fufu ro saudin am dondi nguwu son kuru alamaram zauro yintǝbe waneye sawandin (acute respiratory distress syndrome) (ARDS) ye kudo mbeji kuru extrapulmonary manifestations -a son.
