Saa kada ngawobe kozǝna dǝn, HCoV jili gade gade tulur fodutǝ.
Tarihi kasarrata HCoVye loktu fodutǝnzabe'a (Tewur 1) kasarrata dǝ bayan cinye kuru ilmu cinye ro waljin.
Kuli HCoV-229E buro salakye dǝ zawal yintǝbe tiyi am kwasa zawal yintǝbe zamzǝnabe sandiya sǝtanayen firratǝ suro saa 1966be lan, daji kuru ngawo adǝyen suro lai sel fufu ye shiro WI-38 sayindǝn wuratǝ gozǝ kowono.
Am do sandiya HCoV-229Eye zamzǝna alamawa tantanyi noatabe fǝleyada, suro dǝn kǝla sǝrǝn so, wadiska ikko so, tiyi samma so kuttu fantǝ-a nguwalto lilimtǝ-a, rokko dǝn kuru kange-a kasau zata-a turuna suro ci 10~20% lamarra au kessaye dǝn.
Dare saa 1967ye lan, HCoV-OC43 dǝ awo shiro "organ culture" sayin me dǝn firratǝ kuru ngawo adǝyen kǝrǝng julwa sǝnana nganji sasayin men yita kotǝgǝ men.
Alamawa liyitaribe kam kwasa HCoV-OC43be zamzǝnaye dǝ alamawa do HCoV-229Ebe'a samun ro wallono, sandiye kuru nasha futu kamma zǝkcin me dǝn kwasawa kuli zawal yintǝbe gade jili "influenza A virus" -a "rhinovirus"-asobe dǝga gayertimba wo.
HCoV-229E-a kuru HCoV-OC43-a ndiso dunya samma so ro samtǝgǝna, kuru sandiye kam ro faltayin zaman binǝmye lan na kǝnda dunyabe zauro amusu lan.
Ngǝwuso ro, loktu kuliwa sǝnana kwasa saudinma anyiye kaltayin dǝ magǝ fal ma ro gana wo, daji ngawo adǝyen magǝ indi nǝm dondiye zǝgayin.
Kǝra kǝlanzǝkkobe adammanaye laaye wono, am nganza do sandiya HCoV-229Eye zamzǝna so dǝ tantanyi noata ma zau gǝnyi sandiya citan.
Am dondi do kǝmbafi tiyinzabe duno ba'a ro walzana gana laa bas kwasa zawal yintǝbe cidiyabe zau ma sandiya cita.
SARS, shi doni kwasa nimoniyaben noata ma dǝga gadezǝna dǝ shima wawa kwasabe dalil HCoVye kǝla dǝn zauro bayan saptǝna ma wo tarihi adammanaye lan.
Lamar SARSye buro salakye dǝ saa 2002 ye datǝgǝram lan foduwotǝ Nasha Guangdongbe lardǝ China be lan.
Wawa SARSye dǝye sǝkkǝ lamarra au kessa 8,096 rifot tǝdǝna kuru am 774 cezǝna, lardǝwa kadaro tarratǝgǝ.
Tartǝwu kura kura dǝ dawun ba ro, lamar au kes wo so kes gade indi kura kura suwudin ro tǝmatǝgǝna, loktu kaltǝm luwanzabe kau 4 lan sǝta 7 ro saadǝna kuru kawu kǝn 10 nǝm dondiye dǝn nǝm ngǝwu kuliya be tawatcin.
Am dondi do sandiya SARS-CoV ye zamzǝna badiyaram lan sandiya tiyi sǝrǝn so, kǝla sǝrǝn so, kange so, tiyi kutta dano-a amusu-a sǝtayin, anyiye ngawon yintǝ kǝrawu so, kasau so kazǝyi yintǝbe so sandima alamawa darebe wo.
Mbautǝ na'a koji awo suro buyen shiro "lymphopenia" sayin dǝ'a, cida kǝmattǝnye jarabtǝ batti-a, kuru awo do shiro "creatine kinase" gulzayin dǝye ngǝwutǝ-a, anyi samma ayauwwa au jarawa'a (test) do jawawu kalkal sadimba ma so do SARSye suwudin.
Kasam saktǝram yintǝbe banna, am kasau SARS ye sǝtanamadǝ lan hangal gǝnatuna taidazǝ surain alou do 'epithelial cell gultindǝ`a bu kwasa mbultaye suro tiyiye macrophages gultindiye zauro mebji sandilan.
Suro ci miya 100% am dondizanaye lan ci 20-30% daji cistǝgǝ ngǝla-a injin yintǝbe-a mǝradǝzana.
Zawal yintǝbe cidiyabe dǝn nguron, karewa surobe kada jili karewa surobe kǝmbu nyetǝye so, kǝmattǝn-a kǝntǝliram-a so samma so zamtin kessa zauro zau so lan, adǝ ngǝwuso ro awo shiro 'cytokine storm' sayin dǝ suwudin, kuru adǝye mowonzǝ kam lorjin, taganas ma ro am dondi do tiyinzan duno kwasa dǝ'a gǝrtǝye ba ma so.
Kuli kwasabe dǝ buro salakyen fufu dur kam do buro salakye kwasa dǝye zamzǝnabe lan firratǝ, shi doni Hong Kong ro Guanzhou lan cizǝ bǝlagurozǝna dǝ.
Loktu shima dǝn tai kuro kude, ngǝnǝwu zauro tǝkkǝna nasha kulashi HCoVye ro.
HCoV-NL63 dǝ tiyi tada kǝntagǝ tulurra yen firratǝ au gowotǝ lardǝ Netherlandsye lan suro datǝgǝram saa 2004be lan.
Badiyaram dǝn tiyi nduli sǝnanabe-a, am ngǝlinza lezǝna-a am duno kwasa gǝrtǝbe tiyinzabe ganazǝna do kuru nǝm dondi nasha yintǝbe sandi lan mbeji ma'a soye lan ngǝwu soro tuwangatǝ.
Kǝnza tuttǝ-a kuru kaino fantǝ baa-a, tuno shimye-a, kange-a kuru tuno fufube-a dǝ kwasa do HCoV-NL63ye suwudin dǝn sandima ngǝwu so ro turin wo.
Kulashi naptǝ kǝlanzǝye gadeye kuli shima dǝ kǝnza tada kǝntagǝ uskua do nimoniya sha zǝkcin yen firta sukkuwaltǝgǝna lardǝ Netherlandsbe lan.
Netherlands lan sha asuwatǝ yaye, dunya samma so ro samtǝgǝna au tartǝgǝna.
HCoV- NL63 dǝ shima dalil kwasawa yintǝbe ci miyabe lan ta'adir ci 4.7% yedei suwudin, kuru zaman do ngǝwu ro fǝlangjin dǝ shima badiyaram be ye-a, nǝngǝli-a kuru binǝm-a.
HCoV-NL63 dǝ sha dau luntǝ'a kǝltǝna, kuru shima dau zau sudin lan notǝna dǝ.
Saa shima dǝn, HCoV-HKU1 tiyi konga laa saa 71 yen tutuluwuna, shi doni dalil nimoniya-a tuno fufube buronkiyolaitis gulzayin dǝ'a yen sha litarin rozana ma Hong Kong lan.
Nimoniya nguro lan gotin-a buronkiyolaitis-a ye guron, HCoV-HKU1 dǝ sha asǝma zauro zau'a kǝltǝna.
HCoV-NL63-a, HCoV-229E-a, HCoV-OC43-a yedei, HCoV-HKU1 dǝye dunya samma so lan tuwandǝna, kwasa yintǝbe gana nǝske'a ammo suwudin.
HCoVwa nguro lan tuwandin sandi diyeu anyi samma so zauro tiyi adammanayen kaanza zaa gozayin kuru jili gade ro faltǝ kwasa zauro zai ma saudimba, tajirwa so wakazǝna yaye dalil notǝnyi laaye sǝkkǝ jili HCoV-NL63ye zauro zau ma do China lan kwasa diwal yintǝbe cidiyabe zauro zau suwudin.
Ngǝwuso ro, sa HCoVwa anyiye raktǝ tiyi kamma ro faltǝgǝbe-a kuru tiyi kamman kazǝyi ba ro kǝnǝngatǝbe-a sowandaiyya, raktǝnza kammo illa au kwasa kudobe dǝ ganajin.
MERS-CoV dǝ buro salakyen fufu kam dondi nimoniyaye zauro sha zǝksǝna saa 60'a ye lan firratǝ au gowotǝ saa 2012yen Saudia lan.
Lamarra au kessa lab lan tawattǝgǝna ngǝwuso Gǝdi dawube lan ciwono yaye, lamarra au kessa lardǝwa gaden tuwudǝna do loktu loktu lan am karunguye ro tartǝyin dǝ lardǝwa Europebe-a Tunisia-a lan rifot tǝdǝna.
South Korea lan fǝlangtǝ kura gade wakazǝna saa 2015 lamarra au kessa 186 tawattǝgǝna..
Alamawa nǝm dondibe MERS ye dǝ SARS ye dǝga samun, nimoniya zauro zau ma lan asutin.
SARS yedei gǝnyi, am MERSye sandiya sǝtana ngǝwu so kǝntǝliram nza cidajimba ro waljin, adǝ shima MERS'a gayerzǝ kwasawa HCoVye gade so'a.
Suro am dondizanaye ci 30% ma kozǝna alamawa suro kuttaye fǝlezana, misallo shidada-a fitǝ-a.
Kǝntagǝ Februariye kaunzǝ kǝn 14ye saa 2020 ye lan ku ro kude, lamarra lab lan tawattǝgǝna 2500 samin ye rifot tǝdǝna, kǝrmu ci 34.4% yedei tǝma'ata, MERS-CoV daji kuli kwasabe diwi adammanaye nozǝna shiyeyi ba ro wallono.
Dau dau kǝntagǝ December saa 2019ye lan tai darenzǝ ro kude, jam'u am nimoniyaye sandiya zǝkcin ma doni kwasa SARS-CoV-2'a leyata ma so cidi Wuhan, nasha Hubei, lardǝ Chinaye lan fodutǝna.
Karapka Nǝlewabe Dunyabeye kwasa zawal yintǝbe cidiyabe ma kǝrmaa ro wakajin ma dǝ'a Lamar Nǝlewa Jamaye Duwasashibe do dunya samma so'a zǝksǝna ma sǝ fǝlejio kuru kwasa shima dǝ'a COVID-19 lan bowono.
Kǝntagǝ Marisye kaunzǝ kǝn ǝ me saa 2020 yen, lamarra 90,053 dunya samma son tawattǝgǝna, suro adǝyen ci 3.4% dǝ cejin.
Hubei, China lan kwasa dǝye am cezǝnadǝ kashi 4.2%, amma diyanzaye dǝ 1.2% cezǝ.
SARS-CoV-2 dǝ kwasa yintǝbe zauro zau ma suwudin jili SARS-CoV -a kuru MERS-CoV-a yedei, alamawa fǝlejin dǝye sandima kange, kasau-a yintǝ kǝji ro fandǝm gotǝ baa-a.
Shidadaye am dondi laa son turuna.
Nimoniya shima alama nǝm dondiye zauro zau ma wo kuru raksǝ kwasa yintǝbe zauro duno'a ro waljin.
SARS-CoV-a SARS-CoV-2-a dǝ zauro samin yaye, jam'u kada ro walza daji kǝska yallaye dǝn dalam gade gade ro gasarayin.
SARS-CoV-2 dǝ nǝm zau lan au kamma dondi ro dio men SARS-CoV -a MERS-CoV -a yedei sǝtǝnyi amma kuru kammo faltǝgǝ men sandiya kozǝna.
Am SARS-CoV-2 ye sandiya zamzǝna amma alama fǝletǝ badizanyi ye rifot tǝdǝna kuru adǝye banaǝgǝ dunya ro duwaro tartǝyin.
SARS-CoV-2 - a HCoV'a arakkǝ gabsǝna dǝ'a gǝrenǝm kǝllǝm yellǝmiya, nǝm samunza-a nǝm gade gadenza-a kamma ajabsǝyin kada fǝlejin.
Kǝn tilominzǝ dǝ, loktu bafǝ kaltin dǝ-a kuru loktu kwasa HCoVye gojin dǝ-a dǝ zauro samun.
Lamar adǝ me dǝn, SARS-CoV-2 dǝ shi HCoVwa arakkǝ dǝye noata ma dǝ gowotcin..
Kǝn indiminzǝ, nǝm zau alamawa COVID-19ye dǝ ndikate SARS-CoVye-a HCoVwa diyeu gabsǝna (sandima HcoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 and HCoV-NL63) nguro lan gotin ye'a lan kara.
Mukko fallan, kwasa SARS-CoV-2 dǝ alamawa fǝlejin dǝ sandima jili alamawa HCoVwa nguro lan gotin so lan turin dǝ, surodǝn mbeji alama ngǝla ro notǝnyi fǝletǝ so, alama zau gǝnyi au alama baa so.
Mukko fal dǝn, jum'la gana laa lamarra COVID-19ye zauro zauma ye turin jili lamar kwasa SARS-CoV ye kamma letǝ so, nǝm ngǝwu kamma tawobe dǝ gana cidiyazǝna yaye.
Kǝn yakkǝme, SARS-CoV-2 ye kammo faltǝgǝ dǝ kǝndoramwa do suro halla/alamawa HCoV nguron gotinbe-a SARS-CoVbe-a ndiso fǝlezǝna.
Mukko fallan, kammo faltǝgǝ SARS-CoV-2ye dǝ gananzǝ yaye kammo faltǝgǝ HCoV nguron gotin yedei sǝtǝna.
Mukko fal dǝn, kammo faltǝgǝ SARS-CoV-2ye dǝ ngawo tiyi adammana so yen gaa kozǝnayen fulutin la fulutimba jili kessa SARS-CoV-a MERS-CoV-a yedei dǝ fuwun do tawattǝyin.
Dare dajiram lan, HCoVwa dǝ yedei, SARS-CoV-2 de suro samfǝr najasa au bǝlibe yen mowonzǝ asutin.
Najasa-ci men Faltǝgǝ SARS-CoV-2ye dǝ katap faida'a gowotcin la gowotcimba jili lamar SARS-CoV yedei kǝndawa laan dǝ kulashi fuwubeye fǝlejin.
Awo taganas ma ro notiya tǝraana dǝ shima SARS-CoV-2 dǝ zaman ro lezǝyin wa jili HCoVwa nguron gotun so yedei.
Samma son yaye, alamawa SARS-CoV-2 asutin jili kammo faltǝgǝ so, kamma donditǝgǝ so, kuru suro amma lan tartǝgǝnzǝ so samma faidajin tamoram COVID-19 kǝrmaa ro fǝlangzǝna dǝ notǝ ro.
HCoVwa nguron gotin diyeu samma so gana laa kamma dondizayin kuru adammana so'a ba salina.
Kururam gade men, jire ro waljin adammana so dǝ HCoV wa diyeu anyi'a ba salina.
Gultǝ gade men, indi so wawa HCoVye din soru kǝnǝngatana.
HCoVwa do tiyi adammana soyen kwasa zauro zau sawudin ma-a adammana so do kwasa HCoVye zau tiyinzan waazǝna-a samma ba ro tǝdǝna.
Adǝgai dǝ wakatǝ ro, HCoVwa dǝ tiyi adammana so yen tai daza ngǝwuzayin futu mowonzǝ kǝnda tiyibe dǝ salinna son faltayin ro hatta askǝrra tiyibe raksa kǝriuzayin ro waljin.
Asutǝ adǝ lan, wawa SARS-CoV-2 ye dǝ loktu gǝrjinna son kuru amma sǝtayin au zamjinna son, duluwu do adammana so'a cetto sǝli au tiyinzan napcinye dǝ kura jin.
Zauro tiyi amma sǝli kaanzǝ zǝgǝ gowono maa, kamma ruwunzǝ kortǝ so katappa gade kamma kǝnta daptǝye so dǝ ye tartǝgǝnzǝ dapcimba.
Saa kada ro CoVwa nguro lan gotin dǝ dau jumla adammanaye lan fomzayin, tantanyi noata ma dau am bunza dunowa ye lan sǝsangin.
Kuliwa kwasabe anyi tiyi dabbaye so mǝradǝzanyi.
Adǝro gadezǝna, SARS-CoV -a MERS-CoV -a do zauro kam dondizayin ma dǝ adammana so'a salǝnyi ngǝla ro kuru kam ro fafaltǝgǝnza dǝ loktu ngǝwu ro dǝgayimba.
sandi anyi ma dǝ tiyi dabbayen kǝnǝngatǝ-a ngǝwutǝ-a mǝradǝzana, daji allan tiyi dabbaye dǝn adammana ro kozayin, duluwuwa fal au adǝ'a kozǝna men.
SARS-CoV-2 dǝ halla/alamawanzǝ laa dǝ SARS-CoV/MERS-CoV-a HCoVwa diyeu nguron gotin dǝ'a samun.
Shidǝ HCoVwa nguron gotin so yedei zauro faltǝgǝ butu'a, kǝrmaa dǝ ro.
Adǝgaima, HCoVwa nguron gotin so dǝ'a nǝm zau kam donditǝgǝye lan kozǝna, amma kuru SARS-CoV au MERS-CoV yedei sǝtǝnyi.
Fuwulan do turin raksǝ tiyi adammana soye cotto sǝli kuru tiyinzan fomjin guwom au dabba ndikate dǝn ba ro.
Kau bayan kǝla HCoV futu tiyi dabbawa yen tuwandinye diyendǝro, andeya zauro banajin bayan kǝla ma'ana so, ada au halla dabbawa do HCoV tiyinzan tuwandinye.
Dabba shima awo shiro 'evolutionary host' gulzayin dǝ ro waljin HCoV ro sa sha kamanzǝ laa sha samunna awo siro 'homology' gulzayin dǝ tilojiya.
Kuli kwasabe kaa ram yayya ram shima dǝ ngai dǝn zauro sǝlin ye kuru kam dondizǝyimba.
Adǝgaima, guwom au tankǝ kuli kwasabe rojin dǝ loktu kuru ro kuru datǝ ba ro HCoV rojin.
Kessa indi son, dabba au kam dǝ alamen sha kwasa dǝye sǝtayin kuru HCoV au kuli sha sambǝna dǝ'a sandima tiyinzan sotozayin.
Adǝ ro gadezǝna, HCoV dǝ bǝlin ro tiyi sototǝmaye ro kau tiyi adammanabe ro tǝkkin ro karaa maa, sototǝma bǝlin dǝ'a ngǝla ro sǝlinyi kuru ngǝwu so ro kam dondizǝyin.
Sototǝma dawube adǝ shima naptǝ guwom do shi men adammana'a kuli dǝye suwandǝ zamjin wo kuru katap sototǝma kuraye gowotcin kuli kwasabe dǝ'a kolzǝ ngǝwutǝ men daji kuru adammana so ro faltǝyin, ngal do ammo faltǝyin dǝ allan kurajin.
HCoV ye mowonzǝ kammo faltǝgǝ do fuwu ro kotǝ baa ma ro gayin sa tiyi sototǝma dawube dǝn tartǝgǝ ngǝla suwandǝnyi maa.
Adǝ ro gadezǝna, HCoV so dǝ raksa tiyi sototǝma dawube dǝ salin kuru har tiyi dǝn caman kasharu yedei ro loktu kuruwu ro napsayin.
Jili lamar adǝ lan, sototǝma dawube dǝ guwom au tanki sototǝma ro waljin.
Sapsapno bayan na cizǝnaye dǝye fǝlezǝna lamar au kes SARSye buro salakye dǝ tarihi dabbawa karaabeya letanabe mbeji.
Kulashi ndu kuli dǝ tiyinzǝn mbejiye ngawo dǝn tǝdǝna ye fǝlezǝna am sawur au kasuwu dabbawa ye sadin dǝ tiyinzan anti-SARS-CoV IgG ngǝwu mbeji, tiyi jami gade gabsǝnaye ro wungǝmmiya.
Dabba do shiro 'masked palm civet' sayin dǝ-a 'racoon dog' sayin dǝ-a kasuwu dabbawa ro'abe lan tuwandin dǝ sandima buro salakyen tiyinzan kuliwa kwasabe SARS-CoV'a samun mbeji ro fodutǝna wo.
Mana adǝ duno cuwando sa ngawo dabba 'civet' sayin kasuwu dǝye samma cetǝnaye lan gadero rifot SARSye tuwandǝnyi
Adǝgaima, rifot tuwandǝna 'masked palm civet' karaaye au kulo lan rotǝna do dabbawa ro'a kasuwuye dǝ'a letanyi dǝ ngǝwu so tiyinzan SARS-CoV ba wo, adǝye fǝlejin dabba shima dǝ sototǝma dawubeye naptǝn kara amma shi gǝnyi guwwom au tanki SARS-CoVye wo.
Dabbawa kasuwu Guanzhou ye dǝ ci 80% so tiyinzan awo kwasa kǝriutǝye shiro 'anti-SARS-CoV antibodies' gulzayin dǝ mbeji daa, mowontǝ do jili dabbawa sǝnanaye gade gade kada raksa sototǝma dawube SARS-CoVye ro walzayin dǝ cistǝgǝ baa ro mowonjimba.
Anyi samma so alama sandi sototǝwu darebe SARS-CoVye fǝlezǝna.
Dabba do SARS-CoV sotojin alameye baratǝye batata CoVye zauro karungu ro leyata fǝlezǝna, kuli kwasaye dǝ ro 'SARS-related Rhinolophus bat CoV HKU3 (SARSr-Rh-BatCoV HKU3) gulzayin, shi doni tiyi batata 'horseshoe' sayin dǝyen tuwandin dǝ
Batata'a anyi awo shiro 'anti-SARS-CoV antibodies' gulzayin dǝ tiyinzan mbeji kuru awo shiro 'genome sequence' SARSr-Rh-BatCoV HKUǝ3ye gulzayin dǝye tiyinzan mbeji.
Shi adǝ-a CoV batataye gadeso-a dǝ ci 88 - 92% ro kude awo shiro 'nucleotide sequence homology' gulzayinye dǝ sandi sammaye so jilinzǝ fal.
Kǝra'a anyiye mana do batata so dǝ sandima kuliwa adammana ro kwasa sawudin sotozayin ye dǝ ro furtǝ sadǝ.
CoVwa SARS'a samun (SL-CoVs) so yedei kada tiyi batata so yen fodutǝna, amma sandi samma son fal shiro WIV1 sayin dǝ shima ronzǝ'a tutuluyin tiyi batata dǝyen.
Tiyi adammanayen awo shiro 'angiotensin converting enzyme 2 (ACE2)' sayindǝ shima kuli kwasaye SARs-CoV dǝ'a sǝmoyin.
Kuli kwasabe WIV1 bǝli batatayen tuwandin dǝ shi lan faidatǝ ACE2 batataye-a, civetye-a, adammanabe-a dǝ shi men tiyi ro gayin ro fǝleyetǝ.
Awoye ajabba dǝ, bu am SARSye sǝtana ngatǝ sadin ye dǝ raksǝ WIV1 cejin.
WIV1 dǝ shima durra SARS-CoV'a zauro karungu so dǝ'a wakkiljin tiyi batata soyen, awo 'nucleotide sequence homology' gulzayin dǝ ci 95% nga samun wo.
Nǝm samun ndikate kuliwa kwasabe anyi samma son, WIV1 dǝ shi gǝnyi SARS-CoV sambo kuru batata so dǝ sandigǝnyi guwom au tanki sototǝma buro salakye wo.
Tarihi alaanza ye MERS-CoV-a kuli kwasaye batatabe sandiro CoV-HKU4-a CoV-HKU5 gulzayin dǝ-a jam'u fallan gǝna'ano.
Kuli kwasabe tiyi batataye CoV-HKU4-a MERS-CoV-a ndiso sototǝma au 'host receptor' shiro dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) fal faidatayin naptǝ gaworamye ro.
MERS-CoVye awonzǝ shiro 'RNA-ddependent RNA polymerase sequence' gulzayin dǝ yanza'anawa beta-CoVs batataye lardǝwa Europeye-a Africaye-a zauro karungu nasha tarihinza yen.
Kuwayaye, MERS-CoV roa batata karaaye lan tuwandimba.
MERS-CoV-a durnzǝ shin karungu kuli kwasaye batataye bat CoV-HKU25-a dǝ ci 87% ' nucleotide sequence homology' ye ndikatenzan tilo.
Adǝye fǝlezǝna batata so dǝ sandi gǝnyi guwom au tanki sototǝma MERS-CoVye buro salakye wo.
Mukko fal dǝn, kulashi ilmuye Lardǝ`a Gǝdi dawuben tǝdǝnaye fǝlezǝna kalimowa so dǝ tiyinzan awowa do taganas ro MERS-CoV cenin ma mbeji, kalimowa lardvwa Africaye do Gǝdi dawube furtunza wo'a samma fal.
MERS-CoV ro'a do kuli kwasabe tiyi adammana soyen tuwandin dǝ kǝnza kalimowabe lan firratǝ, adǝye fǝlejin kalimo so dǝ sandima guwom au tanki sototǝma MERS-Covye kura wo.
Hangal gǝnatǝ sǝdǝna, alamawa nǝm dondibe sǝnana amma kuli kwasaye fita ngǝwu kalimowa do dalil ilmuye nankaro sandi ro MERS-CoV tǝkkǝna lan turuna.
