Dalilla do fuwutǝ au fafaltǝ dabbaye bayanjin dǝye fǝlezǝna HCoV-NL63-a HCoV-229E-a dǝ CoVwa batatayen ciyada, kuru kuliwa kwasabe HCoV-OC43-a HCoV-HKU1-a dǝ tiyi dabba jili julwa soyen ciyada.
Rifot tǝdǝna CoV batataye shiro ARCoV.2 gulzayin dǝ. Shi doni tiyi batata North Americaye kala yakkǝ'a ma dǝyen turuna dǝ, alaka karunguye ndi kate sha HCoV-NL63-a fǝlezǝna.
Mukko fallan, HCoV-229E dǝ sha CoV batataye gade sunzǝ Hipposideros/GhanaKwam/19/2008 dǝ-a zauro karungu wo, shi doni lardǝ Ghanaye lan fodutǝna dǝ, kuru kalimo sandima sototǝma ndikate wo ro tǝmatǝna.
Ngǝla ro asutǝ nanka ro, ilmu kǝrmaa ro kǝla dabbawa do HCoVwa sandi men tuwandǝnaye dǝ fig. 1-a tewur 2 lan kasartǝna.
Kulashi kǝla fǝlamtǝ au fafaltǝ yen tǝdǝnaye dalil tartǝgǝ HCoVwa ye ndi kate dabbawa gade gadeyen suro tarihiyen wakajin fǝlezǝna.
Sa HCoV-OC43 dabbawa fatoyen fartǝ adammana so sǝtana dǝ saa 1890 lan, wawa kwasa yintǝbe turuna.
