Alpha CoVwa batataye so dǝ sandiya HCoV-229Eya zauro karungu.
Ndikatenzan kuli kwasabe shiro 'alpaca alpha-CoV' sayin dǝ mbeji.
Shadawa kadaye kuli kwasabe batata lan cizǝ adammana ro faltǝgǝye ngawo satana.
Buro salakyen, adammana so sandima batata so'a leta alpaca so gǝnyi, sau kor kǝnǝnganzaye fal nanka dǝ ro.
Susu dǝ ro, adammana so sandima alpaca'a leta.
Kǝn indimi, HCoV-229E alpha-CoV batataye'a leyata dǝ sandi jilinza ngǝwu kuru tiyi batata soyen kwasa suwudimba, amma alpha-CoV alpacaye dǝye kwasa yintǝbe dabbawa zamtǝna lan sǝkkǝ fǝlangzǝna.
Dare dajiram lan, alpha-CoV alpacaye dǝ tiyi dabbawa ca faton rotǝna do karaa ro waltanayen tuwandǝnyi.
Adǝgai lan, mowontǝ doni alpaca soye HCoV-229E alpha-CoV'a leyata dǝ na adammana soyen cuwanda dǝ rangnye tuluyemba wo.
Mana dǝye yanzǝ dǝ, batata so dǝ kuliya kwasabe adammana soye ngǝwu so sandi lan tuwandin, jili kuli kwasa rebisye so, kuli kwasa Ebolaye so, kuli kwasa Nipahye so-a kuli kwasa Hendrabe'a.
Adǝ nanka dǝ ro, batata soye adammana so ro HCoV-229E daata ro falzayin dǝ awo ajabye gǝnyi.
Na alpha CoV batataye sodǝ naptǝ sandi lan HCoV-229E tuwandǝnayen kasharu yaye, alpaca so-a kalimowa so-a dǝ naptǝ sototǝma dawube do kuli kwasabe dǝ'a adammana so ro falzayin yen kasharu, jili lamar MERS-CoV yedei hak biya.
MERS-CoV dǝ misal zauro ngǝlama faltǝgǝ ndi kate dabbawa gade gadeyen, batata lan kalimo ro kuru kalimo lan adammana so ro.
Tarihi baditǝ au fǝlamtǝ MERS-CoVye tiyi batata soyen dǝ shima sha notǝram buroye wo kuru awowa darebe tuwandǝnaye adǝ ro duno cina.
Batata so dǝ nowata kuli kwasabe ngǝwuwa sawudin, ndikate dabbawa gade gadeyen awo 'genetic fragment' gulzayin dǝ yeyektǝ ro kuru ndi kate dabbawa gade gadeyen kuli kwasabe tartǝgǝ ro.
Kawu kuruwu-a, jami ngǝwu na fallo sapkata-a, mu'amala zauro karinguye suro jamiyen-a kuru raktǝ fartǝbe dunowa-a anyi samma kǝndawa do batata ro kǝjima kuli kwasabe tartǝgǝma shiyeyi ba ro waltǝ ro.
Mukko fallan, MERS-CoV dǝ kalimowa ro yita gattǝgǝna dǝ saa kada.
Kalimowa anyiya zauro sǝli kaanzǝzǝgǝna hatta sototǝma dawube lan cizǝ guwom sototǝma alameye ro wallono.
MERS-CoV dǝ kwasa sǝnana suwudin kuru futu faltǝ jili gade ro waljinye zauro idiyazǝna tiyi dabbawa anyiye lan.
Adammana so ro faltǝgǝnzǝ dǝ tajirwa men waka'ano kuru adammana so dǝ sandi ma sototǝma MERS-CoVye datǝrambe wo, saunzǝ faltǝgǝnzǝ loktu ngǝwu ro dǝgayimba.
Katap kalimowabe MERS-CoV tartǝgǝ lan gowotsayin dǝ ro gadezǝna lan, katap pangolinye, katap laa gowotcin ma mbeji maa, nasha SARS-CoV-2 tartǝgǝye ye dǝn dǝ gadezǝna.
Taganasma ro, beta-CoVwa pangolinbe dǝ zauro dabba pangolin sayin dǝ ro kwasa au nǝm dondi suwudin.
Sandi dǝ wajiya sototǝma darebe beta-CoVwa SARS-CoV-2'a leyata maye, civet so'a samun suro lamar SARS-CoVye lan.
Mowontǝwa kada kǝla tartǝgǝ SARS-CoV-2 ye ndi kate alauwwa au dabbawa gade gade yen, dabba lan adammana ro faltǝgǝye gotin au koltin kulashiya ilmube fuwu lan tǝdinyen.
Kǝn tilomi, batata so dǝ sandima guwom au tanki sototǝma kuli kwasabe SARS-CoV-2'a samunye wo, SARS-CoV-2'a jilinza tilo yedei.
Adammana so dǝ batata so'a kor kǝnǝngaye fal faidatayin ro waljin nǝm sunuri men (dabba duwatǝ) au cidi lanǝm kǝlimi shiro 'coal' gulzayin dǝ tulo men.
Kǝn indime, pangolin so dǝ sototǝma dawube ro walzayin shi doni belin ro kuli kwasabe SARS-CoV-2'a samun shiro tǝkkǝna ma.
Adammana so dǝ kuli kwasabe dǝ dabbawa karaabe yezo-a danza gǝro-a men gozayin.
Dabbawa kada dauwnzan dabbawa fatobe`a so sandiya mowonzǝ SARS-CoV-2 ye sǝtayin.
Sofiyo dabbawa fatobe-a karaabe-a tǝdǝ awo tiyinzabe 'antibody' sayin kwasa kǝriujin ma dǝ kulastaye dǝ amartǝna.
Kǝn yakkǝme, futu buron gultǝna yedei, waltǝm SARS-CoV-2'a kǝltǝ-a kuru na dǝ kaanzǝtǝgǝ-a dǝ jili dabbaye gade kǝn yakkǝme do batata-a pangolin-a ndiso'a letana lan wakawono.
Kulashi badiyaram SARS-CoV-2 ye tiyi dabbawa yen dǝ kuwayaye tǝdinna kara.
Sototǝma dabbaye gade gade so dǝn kasǝn, awowa yakkǝ muhimmi nasha kuli kwasabeye dǝ sandiye zauro faidazayin nasha CoV so banatǝ dabba gade gade ro faltǝgǝ men.
Buro salakyen, zauro faltǝ ngewu sadin suro "RNA replication" ye lan.
Kuliwa kwasabe RNAbe je falla gade so'a gǝrenǝmiya, nǝm ngǝwu faltǝ CoVwa ye dǝ mowonzǝ daraja ganaye lan tai ngǝwu ro yadeye gultin, fafaltǝ saa lan gana yaye ~10-4 yedei ro faltin.
CoV so dǝ tiyinzan awo shiro “proof-reading exoribonuclease" gulzayin dǝ mbeji, sha cintǝ dǝ fafaltǝ naa kozǝna-a, duno gana-a, au hatta faidajimba ro waltǝ suwudin.
Awo hangal gǝrjin dǝ, awo shiro "nucleotide analogue Remdesivir" sayin dǝ ngǝwutǝ CoVye ratsǝ rojin ro noata, diwal 'exoribonuclease dǝ-a RNA-dependent RNA polymerase dǝ-a daptǝ men.
Remdesivir dǝ shima kurun SARS-CoV-2ye zauro faidajin ro tǝmatǝna do litarin jarabtǝna ma wo.
Adǝn yaye, faltǝ CoV sobe dǝ nǝm ngǝwu lan faltǝ sototǝmanzabe'a ci niliyon fal yedei lan kozana.
Adǝ ro kǝllǝgǝ ne, faltǝ dǝ sa CoV so dǝ sototǝmanza'a salinyi maa shima zauro ngǝwujinno.
SARS-CoV do fafaltǝ ngǝwu'a dǝ'a kǝllǝmiya, fafaltǝ SARS-CoV-2ye dǝ shima gana wo, adǝye fǝlejin tiyi adammana soye kǝlo cetto.
Sototǝma gade adammana so'a karungu gade ro napsǝgǝna ro tǝmatǝna.
SARS-CoV-2 ro kǝllǝgǝmiya, adǝgai dǝ MERS-CoV yen waajin, shi doni zauro kalimowa sǝlina au kaanzǝzǝgǝna.
Mana ngai me dǝn maa, gǝrtǝgǝ awo shiro 'genes' sayin ye dǝye kalimi so kurunna SARS-CoV-2 kǝriutǝbe'a faidajimba sǝdin ro tǝmatǝnyi.
Kǝn indimi, 'RNA genome' kura suro CoV soye dǝ banazǝgǝ faltǝ-a waltǝm kǝltǝ-a wakajin, daji adǝgai men mowontǝ fǝlamtǝ ndikate dabbawaye fuwuzǝyin, shi doni luwo CoV wa soye ro zauro kǝji sa kǝndawa so kalkal jiya.
Ngawo adǝye awo do shiro "copious unique open reading frame" sayin dǝ-a "protein functions encoded towards 3' end of the genome" ye-a ye satana.
Kǝn yakkǝme, CoV so dǝ fasal ba'a ro kuru ngǝwu ngǝwu ro 'template' falzayin sa RNA ngǝwu ro sadin ma nzundu "copy-choice" be shi yeyi ba men.
Tiyi sototǝma do naptǝ awo suro dǝn tuskatinye lan dǝgana dǝ, je faltǝ ngǝwu ngǝwu ro wakajin sa CoV RNA kǝratin lan.
RNAwa sandiro "highly homologous full length and subgenomic" sayin dǝ raksa walta kǝlta CoVwa bǝlin satandin.
Shada waltǝm kǝltǝ alamen wakajinye tuwandǝna suro HCoV-HKU1 be-a HCoV-OC43 be-a ndi son, kuru adǝgaima CoVwa jili SL-CoV batataye-a kuru bat-CoV-HKU9-a.
Mu'amala ndi kate kuli kwasabe-a sototǝmabe-a faltǝgǝ au tartǝgǝ ro wungǝmmiya.
Awowa kuli kwasabe wuzǝna yakkǝ somtǝna anyi dawun ba ro, mu'amala kuli kwasabe-a sototǝma kuli kwasaye sǝmoyinnaye ndikate dǝ zauro faidajin nasha faltǝgǝ au tartǝgǝ ndikate dabbawabe lan.
Na allan, waltǝm kǝltǝ SARS-CoVye dǝ shima misal ro gotin, shi doni kartǝ ngǝla fǝlezǝna sa faltǝgǝ bayna dabbawa gade gadeyen wakajin maa.
Kulastǝ gǝretabe do SARS-CoVwa tiyi adammanabe-a civet-a yen tǝdǝna dǝ ro wungǝmmiya, SARS-CoV dǝ tini sototǝma so sǝlin, taganas ma ro sa faltǝ RBDye wakajiya.
RBD suro 'S protein' CoVye dǝ mowoma suro tiyibe dǝ fantayin au mu'amala sadin kuru awowa kwasa kǝriutǝbe tiyi sototǝmaye dǝye tini sandiya karjin.
SARS-CoV lan, RBD shima 'amino acid' kǝn 318 sǝta 510 ro saadǝna dǝ kǝla 'S1 fragment'ye lan, shi doni ACE2 adammanabe ro kǝrtǝyin gawo kuli kwasabe ye nankaro.
RBD SARS-CoVye dǝ raksǝ mowoma ACE2 dabbawa jili gade gadeye asujin, dawu dǝn batata-a, 'civet'-a kuru' racoon dog'-a mbeji, faltǝgǝ ndikate jiliwa dabbaye gade gade kolzǝ wakajin.
Manaye yanzǝ dǝ, 'amino acid'wa arakkǝ njong kwasa kuli suwudin tiyi adammanbe-a civetye-a lan firtǝna suro RBDyen gade gade ro asutǝ kuru diyeu 4 dǝ na shiro 'receptor binding motif gulayin dǝn kara, mowoma ACE2'a mu'amala dio nanka ro.
SARS-CoV civetye dǝ RBDnzǝn faltǝ shiro K479N-a S487T gulzayin dǝ mbeji, shi doni mu'amala "spike protein" be-a mowoma ACE2 adammanabe-a ndikaten mu'amala dio suwudin dǝ.
Ma'ana, 'amino acid'wa ndi anyi sandiya faltǝ dǝ zauro faida'a kuli kwasabe adammana liyo ro.
SARS-CoV-2 dǝ sha SARS-CoV'a mowomanza tilo.
Nǝm gade ci 30% ndikate SARS-CoV-2-a SARS-Cov-a suro 'S1 unit protein"ye dǝye fǝlejin 'S proteinye ACE2 adammanabe'a kǝltǝ dǝ gana bannatǝna.
Tawadǝ ro, kǝra cryo-EMye kǝltǝ adǝye wakatǝnzǝ ci 10 - 20 lan kǝltǝ ACE2 adammanabe-a SARS-CoV S protein be-a kozǝna fǝlezǝna.
Mowoma gǝdima gade faltǝgǝ SARS-CoVye ro mǝradǝtǝna la mǝradǝtǝnyi ro notǝ dǝ tǝraana.
Awo ajabba dǝ, HCoV-NL63 ye ACE2 ro nasha Sye gade men kǝltǝyin.
Mowoma HCoVye gade kada mbeji, misallo "aminopeptidase N" HCoV-229E ro, kuru "9-O-acetylated sialic acid" HCoV-OC43 ro.
Sandi anyi raksa futu CoVwa anyiye adammana so kǝlon kǝnasartana dǝ guljin, ngawo faltǝgǝ ndikate dabbawa gade gadeyen sǝkkǝ tiyi dabbawanzayen gozana.
Mowoma 'cellular'ye ro kǝllǝgǝmiya, tamoram faltǝgǝ HCoVwabe ndikate dabbawa jii gade gadeye dǝ sototǝma gade ro tǝngatǝgǝ-a awowa gade faltǝgǝ dapcin-a kǝla dǝn huwom sǝdin.
Nǝm gade gade "protein"wa sototǝma anyiye ndi kate adammana so-a guwom sototǝma alamen waajin HCoVwaye jili batata so, kalimo so, kuru dabbawa sǝnana julwa yedei so-a yedǝ, kalangai ro walzayin dabba falyen gade ro faltǝgǝ ro.
HCoV so dǝ lamarra do sǝkkǝ sototǝma ro tǝngatayin dǝ ba ro sadǝ kuru lamarra do sǝkkǝ sototǝmaye sandiya dapcin dǝ wurzayin, kǝnasar faltǝgǝ ye ndikate dabbawa gade gadeyen fando nankaro.
Adǝ ro wungǝmmiya, molekyulla do nasha mu'amala kuli kwasabe-a sototǝma-aye asuzayin dǝ zauro sandiya asutǝ faidajin.
Skǝrinin ngǝla kǝla sototǝma ro tǝngatǝgǝyen-a kuru lamarra faltǝgǝ dapcin-a SARS-CoV-2ye tǝdǝna ma ngǝlawo, nzundu zamanye CRISPR dǝ faidatǝ dio dǝ zauro faidajin.
Luwo HCoVwa bǝlinye: badiyaram ro waltǝ.
Nǝm gade gade CoVwa batataye dǝ duluwuwa luwobe HCoVwa bǝlin ro cina.
Mana adǝ ro wungǝmmiya, CoVwa batataye dǝ sandima HCoVwa bǝlin so dǝ'a sasambǝ.
Adǝ ro yira, fafaltǝ duwa duwabe-a 'genetic recombination'-a dǝ sandima fǝlamtǝ HCoVye fuwuro zuzayin kuru naptǝ katapwa faida'a indiye sadin duluwu adǝ lan.
Misallo, awo shiro "novel protein-coding genes" sayin dǝ fando au fattǝgǝ dǝ raksǝ 'viral phenotypes' saashin.
Dawu protinna faida'a SARS-CoV ye dǝn, ORF8 dǝ zauro nasha tiyi adammana liyo be dǝn faida'a ro fantin dǝ, dalilnzǝ dǝ kuliwa kwasaye batataye do SARS-Cov'a leyata dǝ firtǝ tutuluwuna amma sandiye protin ORF8 gade gade nozana.
Hal SARS-CoVye niukǝliyotayid 29 cintǝbe dǝ suro jili do tiyi adammanaben firtǝna dǝn mbeji badiyaram wawa adammanabe dǝn.
Cintǝ dǝye ORF8'a ORF8a-a ORF8b-a ro yekcin, kuru adǝ faltǝ liyo be do sototǝma faltǝ fuwuzǝyin ma ro turin.
Adǝ dawun ba man, SARS-CoV dǝ tarihinzǝ waltǝm CoVwa alfa-a gama-a kǝltaye mbeji, na do nasha sǝnana waltǝm kǝltabe kada fodutǝna tiyi "RNA polymerase" do RNA ro tǝngatǝgǝ na yen.
Nasha'a waltǝm kǝltabbe na'a shiro nsp9 gulzayin dǝ-a, nsp10-a, kuru na'a laa nsp14be-a dǝ fodutǝna.
Adǝgaima, wawa MERS-CoVye turuna dǝ kǝlele waltǝm laiyya gade gaden kǝlta ro fǝletǝna, shi doni tiyi kalimowa Saudi Arabia yen wakazǝna dǝ.
SARS-CoV'a MERS-CoV'a guron, kǝlelewa waltǝm kǝltabe dǝ HCoVwa gade lan turuna, suro dǝn HCoVwa dǝ CoVwa dabba'a gadebe'a kǝltayin.
Kuru adǝgaima sumo'a gǝrtǝ kartǝ ngai kamma dǝ fafaltǝ nyiyatǝnyi suro "viral genome" ye dǝn suwudin dǝ ro, adǝye awo suwudin dǝ kuliwa kwasabe dǝ'a kazǝyi kartǝbe ro sǝtkayin, misallo askǝrra tiyi sototǝmaye dǝ.
Misal tamoramwa anyi be dǝ shima fattǝgǝ datǝ kaamil ORF4ye tiyi HCoV-229E ye lan, adǝ sawunzǝ niukliotide indi cinta.
ORF4 letǝnyi dǝ tiyi batata-a kalimo-a ye lan turin yaye, "alpha-CoV" alpaca ye dǝ ikkoram niukliotayid ye fal dǝ ma fǝlejin, adǝye gǝrtǝgǝ 'frame'ye suwudin.
Dare datǝram lan, fǝlamtǝ (evolution) HCoVwa be dǝ kazǝyi karnobe suro guwom au tiyi sototǝmaye dǝ sha fuwuzǝyin.
Alama nǝm dondiye baa au alama nǝm dondiye gana laa turuna sa batata so CoV soye sandiya sǝtaiyya, adǝye kǝlo ndi kate CoV so-a batata soye-a dǝ fǝlejin.
Batata so dǝ zauro CoV so-a talina nasha futu tiyinzaye tǝnandǝna-a cidajin-a so yen.
Misallo, illawa jawawu kau kwasa dǝ cijin ro tiyi batata soye sango dǝ tai dazǝ nǝm dondi CoV soye saudin dǝ fulujin.
Adǝn kasǝn, cidawa sel yezobe tiyi batata soye dǝ rattǝna dalil na'a awowa sel cejin mowobe NKG2/CD94 dǝ kaltǝgǝyen kuru daraja awo shiro "major histocompatibility complex class I molecules" gulzayin dǝ gana ro fǝletayen.
Ngǝwutǝ "reactive oxygen species (ROS)" be do cidatǝ ngǝwu tiyi batatasoye suwudin dǝye raksǝ ngǝwutǝ CoVye ratsǝ rojin kuru "exoribonuclease"ye gam yasa ye lejin, adǝgai lan kazǝyi kartabe suwudin jili kuli kwasabe zauro nǝm dondi gǝrzǝyin fando ro sa tiyi sototǝmaye ro tǝkkiya.
Jiliwa CoVye zauro nǝm dondi sawudin gade so waltǝm kǝltǝmen fǝlamzana ro waljin, adǝye "novel protein" fando suwudin au alamawa "protein"be fando suwudin yiyi sototǝmaye kǝlo nankaro.
Adǝ ye fǝlejin, luwo au bayantǝ HCoVwa yakkǝye suro saa findi kozǝnaye dǝn dǝ wawa men wakawono ro.
CoV so dǝ tiyi guwom au tanki sandiya sototǝma jili batata so kalimo soyen nǝm dondi saudimba au saudiyaye gana.
Sandi dǝ taidazana ngǝwuzayin, tiyi sototǝmanzaye sandiya luwalajimba ro.
Na adǝ lan ashir am alama nǝm dondiye tiyinzan ba asutinn-a kuru awo do tiyi adammanasoyen nǝm dondi zauro zau suwudin dǝ kara.
Alamawa nǝm dondibe zauro zau dǝ ngǝwuso ro dalil cidatǝ ngǝwu askǝrra tiyibe-a kuru awo shiro "cytokine response" sayin do cidatǝ askǝrraye dǝ duno'a jin wo son, banna fufube dǝye tǝrayin.
Adǝ ro gadezǝna, tiyi gotǝwu alama nǝm dondibe fǝlezzanyi soyen, cidatǝ au katap gotǝ askǝrra tiyibe dǝ ngǝwu tǝ CoVye'a yektǝna.
Fasal cidatǝ au katap gotǝ tiyibe yektǝbe dǝ tamoramwanzǝ faidajin waniye mbeji nasha kurun dio anti-SARS-CoV-2 be lan.
Jawawu "interferon"be dǝ taganas ro dunowa tiyi batata soyen.
Adǝye fǝlezǝna, "type I interferon" badiyaram sa kamma SARS-CoV-2ye sǝtana dǝn ikko dǝ adammana so ro faidajin.
Adǝ ro nzǝra lan, waltǝm sango "NLRP3 inflammasome" tiyi batatsoye dǝ batti/cidajimba/faidajimba.
Dalil adǝ futa men, MCC950 lan "NLRP3 inflammasome" daptǝ dǝ waniye kurun COVID-19ye dio ro faidajin.
Fǝlangtǝ au luwo SARS-CoV-2be dǝ duluwu fal do SARS-CoV-a MERS-Cov-a cizana dǝ zǝgayin.
Beta-CoV batatabe dǝ ci 95% "nucleotide homology"nzabe SARS-CoV'a jili fal faidatayin, kuru adgaima CoV-batatabe do ci 96% "nucleotide homology"nzabe SARS-CoV-2'a tilo.
Dabba shiro 'civet' sayin dǝ-a dabbawa gade so'a suro kasuwube dǝn sandiya tuwandǝna kuliwa kwasabe SARS-CoV'a samun tiyinzan mbeji gozana fomzain, sototǝma dawube tinibe SARS-CoV-2 be dǝ kǝrmaaro fodutǝnyi.
Beta-CoVwa 'pangolin'be zauro SARS-CoV-2'a "homologous" tuwandǝna, daji adǝye fǝlejin 'pangolin' dǝ naptǝ sosotǝma dawube ro waljin au beta-CoVwa 'pangolin'be dǝ raksǝ waniye awo shiro "gene fragments" sayin dǝ kaanzǝwu cin jili SARS-CoV-2ye darebe dǝ ro.
Korowa kuwa yaye mbeji yaye, shada do SARS-CoV-2 dǝ adammana sǝtandǝbe dǝ ba wo, walau nadibe ro au tajirwa men.
CoVwa so dǝ ba isa noata ro walzana dalil fǝlangtǝ SARS-CoV-2 karungube dǝ ro.
Kǝra au kulashi kǝla CoVwa batatabe-a dabbawa gadebe-a tǝdǝna dǝye notǝnde kǝla faidawa badiyaram kwasawa tartǝyin au faltǝyinbe-a kuru guwom au tankiwa HCoVwa be-a tiyi adammana soyen tartǝgǝnzǝ falzǝna.
Dalilla dunowabeye fǝlezana SARS-CoV-a, MERS-CoV-a, SARS-CoV-2-a samma so badiyaramnza batatabe mbeji kuru adammana ro falzayin sototǝma dawube men.
Nǝm dondi au kwasa SARS-CoVye dǝ kǝltǝ ndikate adammanbe-a civetwa kasuwubeye soye men ciyono daa, kasuwuwa dabbawabe dǝ zaktǝ-a civetwa ronza ro yezo-a dǝ wawa SARSbe dǝ tamozǝyin.
Dalil caye dǝ men, 'pangolin' soye kasuwu dabbawabe dǝn ba ro tǝdin tartǝgǝ tiyi dabbawaye men kaltǝgǝ nankaro, jiliwa beta-CoVwa pangolinbe kada SARS-CoV-2'a leyata fodutǝna nanka dǝ ro.
SARS-CoV-2 adammana ro pangolin men faltǝin la faltǝimba kuru futu wi men faltǝin dǝ kulashiwa fuwu lan tǝdin lan asutin.
Mukko fallan, MERS-CoV dǝ tiyi kalimowabe lan loktu kuruwu ro dǝgana.
Kalimowa anyi nasha lenǝm areyen zauro faidazayin, kuru sandi futa men da-a, cam-a, karai-a, kuru kunduli-a tuwandin am fato'be ro.
Sandi kalimowa so dǝ Gǝdi dawube-a Africa-a lan zauro ngǝwu.
Advye sǝkkǝ kalimowa samma so MERS kaltǝgǝ nanka ro yezo dǝ mowonjimba, futu dabbawa karaabe ro kasuwuwa Chinabe lan tǝdǝna dǝ yeyi, tartǝgǝ SARS-CoV-a SARS-CoV-2be-a kaltugǝ nanka ro.
Fǝlangtǝ MERSbe gade dabtǝ nankaro, duluwu kǝske do shi futa men kalimi MERS-coVbe kalimowa ro tando nankaro gotǝna ma ngǝla wo, katapwa gade tartǝgǝ kuli kwasabe daptǝye gotǝn kunten.
Kuliwa kwasabe anyi ba ro dio andero tiyerǝna daa, jiliwa gade waniye solu fǝlangtǝ sawudin.
Jiliwa CoV soye raksa kwasa sawudin ma kada karaa lan fomzayin.
Taganas ma ro, CoVwa batatabe so do raksa kwasa au nǝm dondi sawudin so dǝ jilinza ngǝwu.
Duluwuwa kada mbeji sandi men CoVwa kwasa au nǝm dondi sawudin anyiye fǝlamza kuru walta kǝltayin ma, adǝgayin men CoVwa bǝlin do zauro faltǝyin ma kuru/au kǝrmu adammana so ro sawudin ma fuwu lan soluyin.
Ada dabbawa karaaye gǝrobe na'a laa Chinabe lan tǝdin dǝ koltǝna ma ngǝla wo, kǝla kǝlta au mu'amala ndikate adammana so dabbawa so-a ye mǝradǝtǝnyi fulutǝ nankaro.
Awowa SARS-a, MERS-a, COVID-19-a futa men turuna dǝye sǝkkǝ, dawari ngǝla-a kuru fasal katap goabe-a ngalwo-a gǝnaata mbeji ma ngǝla wo.
Tawadǝ ro, kuliwa kwasa sawudin kada dunya lan loktu kuruwu ro kasharu.
Guwom au tankinza alameye lan kasharu adǝgai do hatta duluwu awo laa gadero cambaltǝm kotabe sowandayin.
Batata so dǝ hallanzaa kada tartǝgǝ kuliwa kwasabe banazǝyin ma mbeji yaye, duluwu adammana soye batataso dabbawa karaaye gadeso-a letayin dǝ gana ro tǝdǝ kuru am soye kǝla fatǝgǝ sandiro cintuza.
Dabbawa so ro sambi so ro shim ikko dǝ mbu ro walzǝna na CoV so kǝnǝngatayin-a kuru sototǝmanza alameye au karaaye so asutǝ ngǝla fando ro, adǝye faidajin nasha faltǝgǝ ndikate dabba-a adammana-aye kaltǝgǝ-a kuru fuwu lan fǝlangtǝ kaltǝgǝ-a ro.
Tamotǝram lan, duluwu do zauro "viral zoonosis" (kuli kwasabe dabba futamen gotǝ) kaltǝyin dǝ shima adammana soye na'a guwomwa au tankiwa kuliwa kwasa sawudin anyiye ro cintutǝ dǝ.
Awowa sǝnana do badiyaram SARS-CoV-2be fǝlejin dǝ kuwayaye ba.
Kǝn fal me dǝ, batata so dǝ kuli kwasabe SARS-CoV-2be din pangolin so ro falzayin maa, awo wutiya sandǝna dǝ shima kǝnda wi son batata so-a pangolin so-a ye na fallan kasharu.
Kǝn indi me dǝ, batata so dǝ nasha adammana ro faltǝgǝben katap kura gowotsayin maa, futu adammana soye batata so-a letayin dǝ notǝna ma ngǝla wo.
Kǝn yakkǝ me dǝ, dabba laa kǝn yakkǝ me shima sototǝ ma dawu be jirebeye mbeji maa, futu jiliwa gade-a letayin adammana-a, batata-a, pangolin-a kunten dǝ asutǝna ma ngǝla wo.
Dare datǝram lan, dabbawa kada hatta dabbawa fatoben kunten sandiya SARS-CoV-2ye mowonǝ sǝtayin daa, faltǝgǝ shim ikkobe-a dim kurube-a ndi so tǝdǝna ma ngǝla wo.
Batata, pangolin, au dabba gade ro wallono maa, SARS-CoV-2 au kuli kwasabe sha sambǝna ma do sandi zauro samun dǝ mowonzǝ fuwulan sototǝmanzǝye tiyi lan fodutin ro tǝma'ata.
Kulashiwa lejin ma do nasha adǝlan tǝdinye zawal fǝlamtǝ SARS-CoV-2ye tiyi dabbawabe dǝ raksǝ sutuluyin, dalilla faidajin nasha COVID-19 tiyi adammana soyen fautǝ-a kaltǝgǝ-a kunte.
Kaida kulashi kǝla COVID-19 ye dǝga bǝlintǝgǝ dǝ "kwasa tǝmatǝgǝna ma"-a "kwasa tawatkata ma"-a ye dǝ zauro faida
Yim 6 February 2020, cidawu de ye kashimo shawari ye kulashi-a kurun diwo-a ye kǝla koronabairos bǝlin 2019 ye (2019-CoV) ye tartǝgǝ nzǝ ye dǝn lǝbsana, kuru kashimo adǝ ye ilmu nde-a nzukolto kǝla futu kwasa dinaye adǝga dina samman kǝriwtǝye cina.
Adǝyeyi ma, kwasa koronabairos 2019 (COVID-19) ye dǝ kwasa dǝwo bǝlin, kǝla fatǝnde-a ilmunde-a dǝ gana ganan tǝrain lǝatar kulashi kǝrmaro tǝdin-a ilmu cida liyitariye-a men, adǝ nankaro, katabwa kulashi-a kurun diwo-a ye so dǝ ye sambiso ro fafaltin.
Suro watiya adǝyen, jawawu koro la kǝla kashimo ndeyen yiyena, kuru kaidawa bǝlin kǝla kulashi liyitariye kǝla "kwasa tǝmatǝgǝna"-a "kwasa tawatkata"-a ye dǝn yiyena lǝatar kulashi-a kurun diwo-a bǝlin yen kǝla COVID-19 ye dǝn COVID-19 (seventh version) shi dǝwo ne Komiti Nǝlefa lardǝye lardǝ China ye cina ma dǝ.
Suro December 2019 yen, kwasa coronavirusye bǝlin 2019 ye (2019-nCoV) dǝ yt sǝkǝ falangtǝ wazǝna, shi dǝwo ne kǝrmaro maila ro sha kwasa koronabairos ye 2019 (COVID-19) lan buwotin dǝ kuru kuli kwasabe dǝ sha kwasa yintǝye zauro zaw coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) lan buwotin.
Yim 11 March 2020, WHO ye COVID-19 dǝga kwasa dinaye ro mawwono.
Tartǝgǝ SARS-CoV-2 ye dǝ fulutǝ ro, cidawu nde ye kashimo shawari ye nagaduye satandana kuru shi dǝwo ne onlayin lan lǝbsana suro kulashi kurun matǝye askǝrra ye dǝn yim 06 February 2020.
Kawu lǝbtǝna wo so zauro hangal jamaye gǝrzǝna.
Adǝyeyi ma hangal gǝnatǝ, kǝla COVID-19 dǝ kwasa bǝlin yen, kǝla fatǝnde-a ilmunde-a dǝ gana ganan tǝrain lǝatar kulashi kǝrmaro tǝdin-a ilmu cida liyitariye-a, adǝ nankaro katabwa kulashi-a kurun diwo-a ye so dǝ sambiso ro bǝlintǝyin.
Misallo kashimo kulashi-a kurun diwo-a ye kǝla COVID-19 yen dǝwo Komiti Nǝlefa lardǝye lardǝ China ye sutuluwuna dǝ (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), dawu 16 January 2020 lan sǝta 3 March 2020 ro suwudǝna ǝn, adadu jumla lǝbtǝ kashi tulur ye sutuluwuna kalmawa la faltǝna ro.
Kǝrma dǝ kashimo ndǝ ye kǝla dǝn Zhou et al. So ye manazana, sandiye shawari bu gotǝna dǝ ye darajanzǝ asutaye saudǝ lǝatar ilmunza liyitaye ro.
Cidanza dǝ ye kashimo nde dǝro hujja serana kuru nzukolto faida kǝla kwasa dinaye dǝro dina samma so ro sǝdǝna.
Ande ye chidanza taida dǝga ardinyena kuru askǝrande fǝlenyena.
Adǝyeyi ma, cidanza dǝ ye bǝlintǝgǝ mǝradǝzǝna futu kulashi bǝlin-a kurun diwo-a kǝla COVID-19 (Trial seventh version) dǝ ye fǝlezǝna dǝyeyi kuru nazaruwa bǝlin-a
Bakta kǝntulur (3 March 2020) ye fǝlezǝnadǝ yeyi, kwasa tǝmata dǝ tawattǝgǝ ro awowa ilmu kwasa tartǝgǝyin ye falnzǝ tuskatǝyin rokko dǝn awowa ndi sheda liyitaye-a bayan ilmu kwasa tartǝgǝyin ye dǝ baro walwono wa:
Bayan Nzundu Kwasa Tartǝgǝyin ye : (1) bayan bǝrni Wuhan ye ro bǝlaro tǝna ye-a nabtǝna ye-a kuru bǝlamashi nzǝ-a ye, aw ngurowa gade COVID-19 fǝlangzǝna so-a suro kawu 14 kozǝna dǝ yen kawu alama kwasabe dǝ buro hawal yin badizana dǝn, (2) bayan kǝla kwasawa tartǝgǝyin ma SARS-CoV-2 ye ro letǝgǝye (with positive nucleic acid test); (ǝ) bayan kǝla kam kange aw kwasa yintǝye alama fǝlezǝna-a ro letǝgǝna bǝrni Wuhan-a mashinzǝ-a lan, aw ngurowa gade dǝwo kwasa COVID-19 ye falangzǝna suro kawu 14 yen tǝn kawu bǝro hawal alama dǝ badizana yen,   (4) bayan kǝla am tawadǝro kwasa dǝ ye sǝtana ro letǝgǝnaye (≥ 2 kwasawa kange ya kǝllatǝ kuru/aw alama kwasa yintǝ ye suro mawu 2 yen fǝlezǝna ma gana lan, alam foto, cidaram, aji muwontiye, gade gabsǝna-a).
Alamawa liyitari Turin: (1) kange-a/aw Alamawa yintǝye; (2) foto alamawa COVID-19 ye sǝtana ye; (ǝ) adadu jumla bu dǝwo shiro white blood cell gultin dǝ ye dǝ kalkal, fulutǝna, aw adadu or reduced lymphocyte ye dǝ loktu badiyaram dǝ man ganazǝna.
Kwasa tawatkata kulastǝ dǝ lǝatar kwasa tǝmata ye dǝwo awowa adǝ ye falnza sheda kwasa y-a aw ngaltǝ buye-a futu adǝ yeyi ro: (1) real-time PCR test dǝ SARS-CoV-2 mbeji ro fǝlezǝna; (2) viral whole genome sequencing dǝ zauro kwasa bǝlin koronabairos samǝn ro fǝlejin (ǝ) positive for the specific IgM antibody dǝ mbeji kuru IgG antibody to SARS-CoV-2 ye suro serum test yen mbeji; aw  SARS-CoV-2-specific IgG antibody dǝ ye ba lan faltǝ mbeji ro waltǝ, aw titer dǝ habtin gade gade ≥4 ro suro kashi ngatǝ ye dǝn kashi zauro zawye dǝga kozǝna ro.
Rangnye ruyen futu real-time PCR test nucleic acid ye dǝ suro yintǝram aw bu gotǝna dǝ ye dǝ lǝbtǝ kǝn ndimi ye dǝro tǝrana (18 January 2020)-a kǝn yakkǝmi (22 January 2020) -a so ro.
Bu gotǝmen kwasa asuta dǝ lǝbtǝ kǝn diyewmi dǝro tǝrana (27 January 2020)-a kǝn uwumi (8 February 2020)-a; kuru daji Hujjawa bu ngaltǝ ye dǝ lǝbtǝ kǝn tulurmi dǝ ro tǝra.
Nzunduwa adǝ lǝatar kulashi ma so dǝye kasadǝnza lan kǝla optimal nucleic acid detection kit dǝga kulastǝ dǝ nagaduro kulastǝ ro, kuru man galtǝ yintǝram-a buye-a son, shi dǝwo ne awo ngaltǝye gade mbeji ro sǝdǝna ma, kuru balimi kwasa kǝriwtǝye tiyi ye mbeji ma dǝ kaida tawatkata ye dǝro kudo dǝ kasadsǝna ma dǝ.
Ngawo adǝyen, shaidawa kada mbeji andero taksǝyin kǝla am dondi dǝwo alama fǝlezain-a fǝlezainmba-a so dǝro hangal gǝnatǝ ro.
Adǝ nankadǝro, flow chart of Zhou et al. so yedǝ bǝlintǝgǝ, dalil dǝ sandiye kam dǝwo alamawa liyitarin asutin ye Shi lan ba dǝga "tajirwa gana" ro kamza kolzana dǝro.
Fasal daraja yoye dǝ ye mǝradǝ kulastǝ ye mbeji cida liyitariye-a nazaru fuye-a lan.
Dare daji la men, shaidawa kǝla tilowa ro gade nguwu isayin ro tǝmanyena kuru kǝratuwu so wa buwonyena bayan nguwu ro sadǝ ro.
