World Health Organization ye COVID-19 dǝ kwasa dǝwo dina samma ye ro bawwono.
Yim Larafawa, World Health Organization (WHO) ye falangtǝ kǝrmaro wajin COVID-19 ye dǝ — kwasa dǝwo coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 ye suwudin ma dǝga — kwasa dina samma so ye ro bawwono.
Son yayi kalma dǝwo "pandemic" dǝ mananzǝ futu kwasa dǝ kura ro tartǝgǝna dǝ bas yayi, nǝm tajirwa kwasa musamman ye gǝnyi, WHO ye mǝradǝ gomnatiwa so dǝga buwotǝ kǝla dǝn katab gotǝye mbeji:
"Lardǝwi yo so raksǝ letǝram kwasa dinaye adǝga faljin.
Sa lardǝwa so dǝ ye kulassan asuzaiyya, ngalzaiyya, kurun sadiya, kozaiyya, sursuri dǝ zasaiyya, kuru amza sabsaiyy kǝla bana tǝ dǝyen," Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus ye wono, kasazadla WHO ye.
"Ande ye zauro zǝktǝkǝna kǝla futu tartǝgǝ -a nǝm zaw ǝd-a kuru futu abi ma kǝla dǝn tǝdǝnyi ye dǝn."
Futu Dr. Tom Frieden ye gulzǝna dǝn, ngawon kazadala formerly the director of the United States' ye daudinzǝ kwasa kǝriwtǝye-a katǝgǝye-a ye, kwasa dinaye dǝ "tǝmmaro tǝmatǝgǝnyi" wono.
Shi ye wono, suro jawaw la CNN ye lǝbsanaye lan suro February yen, "tantayi lan nguron, Kuli kwasabe yintǝ ye jili wi ma sursuri nzǝ sa fǝlangzǝnan tayi dina dukso ro tartanze ro kuden tǝanyi."
Ghebreyesus ye kururam jili tilowa bayanzǝna, wono "ande ye ngaltema kwasa dinaye koronabairos ye tarzǝyin ruyende."
Shi ye waltǝ wono, "kuru ngaltema kwasa dinaye dǝwo raktǝ sha loktu falyin katǝgǝyin ma ruyende."
