Tajirwa kasuwa Covid- 19 be na cidaben kaltǝbe daǝga tartif nzǝlifobe gotǝbe kuru mundǝ nalewabe kuli kasuwabe coronavirus bedǝga kaltǝbe.
Kataf ngalau tajirwa nacidaben kaltǝbedǝ futǝ cidadǝga adutǝban kara, tajirwadǝ jiliwiro zamcin ammasoa kuru cidawu duno gana samma jiliwiro sandiya COVID- 19 zamjin.
Huwuma lardǝ U.S. sha Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA), lan notǝnadǝ cida tajirwa gana a dǝ sandima jama'a cidawu gafsǝna duwan kǝlakǝlzainbawo adǝbe sǝkǝ musko tultǝso faton naftǝso gafsǝnanzaga dǝ sandima kataf kǝla kaltǝbe
Cida'a tajirwa kambai adǝ shima jama'a COVID-19 zamzǝna tǝmatǝna so a kǝla faksana.
Anyi sandima cidawu jama mewua sambisoro kǝla-kǝlzainma alamanna Marantso kasuwuso gafsǝnanzǝga cidazainmasowo.
Kuffu adǝn tajirwa kaltǝdǝ shima kataf nzǝlifobe sandǝna gotǝdǝ shima naksamman naftǝso watiska yikǝminna kǝnaza zaktǝso kuru kǝlanǝmma kam COVID-19 karewa kǝla katǝben faidatǝso.
Huwuma OSHA be cidawu litabega njim kaminnegadǝ am ndoyi kǝlanzaga tajirwaro hatǝnamaro gozǝna sambisoro sǝro tajirwaben kasheru kam kasuwa a kasuwa ba tǝmatǝna tǝmatǝnyiya samma kǝla-kǝlzain.
