Kasuwa amro tartǝyindǝga kaltǝro dawori kaltǝbe gotadǝ Gomnati lardǝbega dalamuwabe shaworin kara.
Muradǝ wawabero kataff gotǝbedǝye surolan kasuwadǝbe tartǝga fulutǝga lamkate cidawubenga jamabega nzǝlifo lamarra kasuwube ga sammalan flube.
Kasuwadǝ isǝ kor-kor lamarra kasuwubedǝ nadanadǝn nakojiro waljiya kataf gotǝnamadǝga zamjin.
Tartif tajirwa kaltǝbedǝ fǝtǝ gotindǝ shima namkambonza la'atarrowo futǝ huwuma nzǝlifobe a nalewabega kaltǝbe faidanzǝ.
Sa COVID -19 gǝrtǝbaro tǝdinbaro waljiya kataf sha kaltǝbe ngalauwa gotin daji daredajiramro karewa nzǝlifo kǝlabe alan gotǝ faidatin.
Zundu kaltǝbe gotindǝbe sǝron cidawu a kulero tǝkin cida samunnam tajirwa hal cidamadǝbelan gawetin baro kuru sulhu muradǝtǝndǝga tawattǝgaso.
kaltǝ nasha kǝrmai bedǝ faltǝ tǝwandin fasal cidabega tartifzǝga faltǝlan mǝradǝ cidawubeben kotǝmaben.
karewa kǝlanǝmga nzǝlifobe shima kǝskewo susumundǝma au kaltǝ kǝrmaibero, amma banasǝdin nasha su au darajala haftǝ kaltǝlan.
kataf kǝla nzǝlifobe samma tangartǝ gotin futǝ cida mabe tajirwa cidanzǝbega kalkalzǝnalan (alamanna cida fufubegairo) kalakalo kǝnasartǝro, kǝlakǝlan ninitǝga, liwoga kuru faltǝga mburo waljiya, futǝ sandǝnaro tuluwoga, kadaubaro sha gǝnatǝga au nasandǝnan koltǝga koltǝga wande kasuwabe zamzǝgǝyiro.
Futǝ huwuma lamarra kǝrmaibe nalewaye lardǝ U. S wono shima sanya hal tajirwabe ganawo cidawu gomnatibega bana wunza zamjindwo.
Tartiffa muradǝtǝnama donyi na'a cidaben kǝlakaltǝbedǝ sandima kǝla-kǝlan musko atultǝ, cidawu a zazzauro tǝkǝ sa sandi dondiga fatolan naftǝ, fufuwa nzǝlifoye diwaldǝ shima sa kasau au zasara sa'am au watikacidǝmma zaktǝ, dina au tawulla dawortǝ kalbo nagadero kotǝbega kaltǝ, cidawuro wande awo gadela n wande faidatai sandiro fǝletga kǝla-kǝlan kor-kor nza fraza kaliworo kǝndoso gafsǝnanza.
Sasǝrtǝga kǝla-kǝla kǝndoga kuru am kasuwabe zamzǝnadǝga kuwulero nzǝko a adǝ shiye kataf ngalau cidawu a kasuwu a kusottowa gafsǝnanzǝ a nzǝlifob.
Huwma lardǝ U.S. sha Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) be tartiffa cinaladǝn cidama kasuwa fufube alamram na gojiadǝ fato nafsǝ hatta sa sha kange a alamaram zǝgabe sha koljiga, kuru alamaram gade a so ta'adir awa fidin lokko diyaube yiro kange dǝgǝ fulutǝnaro daiya, kataf nǝmdondibedǝ raktǝ faltin sambiyayiro, cidamaro wadatǝ fato nafzǝ ha sa gazǝnaro daworo, kuru kǝmanzǝbe fasaldǝga notǝnzǝn mbejiro walzǝ.
Futǝ huwuma OSHA beladǝn cida tajirwa daudau adǝ sandima kǝla-kǝlan kǝlakǝltinma kuru ganazǝ yayi kafa arakǝbe tǝwal lamkatero nzǝko(1.8 m) lamkate jama'a kam kasuwa COVID- 19 zamzǝna nozaiben, kuru waniye kasuwa SARS-CoV- 2 zamzǝna dalil ksawa dǝbe naftǝramdǝga zamzǝndǝbe sǝkǝ, au am la karǝngǝ alan bularo lardǝga diyabe kasuwa COVID-19 tartǝna au tai dazǝ zamzǝnaro lezana.
Anyi sandima cidawu jama'a mewu a sambisoro kǝla kǝlzainma alamanna Malumma Marantabeso, munduwuso sandima awo adǝbe nguwro zamcin dalil sandiga cidawu ngǝwa a jama'a ngǝwuwa kǝla kǝlzaindǝwo. kataf maila adǝga kaltǝbedǝ shima cidawu dondiso dǝga fato naftǝwo kuru cikǝmobe nandi samma kǝla kǝllo naftǝbega faltǝ, bularo jiliwi yayi kallodim na kasuwa COVID- 19 fulezǝnaro letǝ wattǝgaso mbeji kuru cidausobe kǝlayewa kǝla-kǝlan fatǝyin tajirwa kasuwa COVID-19 fatǝ gafsǝnanzga samma mbeji sǝro kataffa kǝla nzǝlifobeladǝn kuru mǝradǝ kambe awo anyilan faidatǝbe murdǝtǝnadǝ sandima; kǝmaje muskobe (glove) gǝmaje (gown) jembu a gafsǝnanzǝga.
cidawu nasha tajirwalan dasnamasodǝ sandima awo fufuwa kalcilan fadatǝ muradǝzana mawo.
kam sǝro maraben dondijiya kataf ngalau gotǝ cidawu a fasinja gafsǝna kaltǝbedǝ shima kadǝga jama'a gade a yaktǝwo , cidma marabe faldǝ shima kam dǝga rawijin kuru zambua awo gade gafsǝnalan faidatin diwal kǝlanzǝ nzǝlifobelan.
Cidama marasamiyedǝ sa kamdondi madǝga hadarcin au lejinna shiye jo muskobega sǝkǝ adǝgaiga kǝndodǝ sha kasuwabe kǝntalan kǝlanzǝga sǝliwin alamanna kangeso kasauso kasuwa yintǝbeso sammalan.
Jo muskobega gafsǝnanzǝgadǝ sha jaga tajirawa kaltǝbero fitǝ adǝgaiga kǝndodǝ nǝmkaliwo au kadauba samma katǝ tǝwandin. mara njibe kasuwube mara fasnjabeso sammalan tajirwa kaltǝyin diwal bularo a nyi dondiro wallamma koltǝben kuru kǝlanǝmma kulero nzǝko alan adǝgaima cidawu nalewabe sǝro marabedǝro ita notǝ nyilan alamaram kange a gafsǝnanzǝgabe mbeji bayantǝlan.
Lafutta maro lamarra nalewabedǝga na kam dondidǝ kulero danaladǝn dǝrinǝm kuruson kunten. Maranta'a na nduli saftǝbesoldǝn Huwuma CDC shawori loktǝ ganaro zaktǝbega cina na dǝga kaliworo kǝndo akuru wande kasuwa dǝga jamaro tartǝnyiro kaltǝro.
Sa alamaram kasuwa anyi tartǝbe tǝwandiga naftǝramlan kataf tǝwallaro kǝnabeso samnoso gafsǝnanzǝga haramtǝnyin loktǝ ganarom kuru cidaram nalewabe taganasbega dawartǝ gatǝyin nduli sǝnana alama kasuwabe tiyinzan fǝlenzǝnamadǝro.
Loktǝ kasuwa taidazǝna tartǝyinbe alama nguro au bulalan fodutiya kataf tǝwallaro datǝbe ngawodǝman marataos cotro zaktǝ. loktǝ alan cidawu nzǝlifoyesoye tǝkin kuru Huwuma CDC beye kataf nalewabega gozǝ tajirwa kasuwadǝmen wajin dǝga kaljin.
Cidawu nzǝlifobe do kam kasuwa COVID-19 zamzna muamala sadǝna madǝbe shawori duwasashibe mundǝ nalewabe dǝga zǝga kǝlanzǝga sǝliwin.
Kǝla a kǝlladamaro walonowa shiye bel nzǝso dǝga diwal tultǝben sha kadaubaro sǝdǝ futǝ fatolan faidatin dǝbeyiro kuru kataf ferno ngalau kasuwa dǝga kaltǝyin diwal nzǝlifo kǝlanǝmbeladǝn kǝmaje tultǝso samma mbeji.
OSHA be cidawu nalewabe a gǝnanaram kaminne adǝ sandima na'a kojiro tajirwabe zarafcinno.
