Cidawu donyi Sandima tai dazǝ zamjinmasdǝ cidanzaga itagatsain tartiffa nuso mowobe au saftǝbesoma am donyi kasuwa COVID 19 zamzǝnaro notǝmab au tǝmatǝnalan gozaindǝn kara.
Fasal Aerosol bedǝbe sǝronzǝlan loktǝ alamaram fǝlentǝbe a kasauwa gafsǝnamanzǝga.
Tajirwa kura cida njim kaminbega wuzǝnadǝ shima kamin kam kasuwa COVID-19 zamzǝna au tǝamatǝna saftǝso lan mbeji. Kurusolan munduwu gǝnanaram am kasuwa COVID-19 zamzǝnam sha kuwulero tǝkinmasodǝ saftǝyindǝyen mbeji.
Nǝm Goinyi ba nasha kaziyi kasam sandǝna tartif nalewabega njim gǝnanaram kaminnabegalan.
Awo ngallema dǝga tartif kauwa nzǝlifobe sana kǝn yakkǝmi dǝga gotǝn.
Huwuma World Health Organization (WHO) shaworia cina kam dondi bulin ishinna kuru sandi dinadǝga yaksa waniye kasuwa COVID-19 sǝdanaro tǝmatǝna dǝga. Nzǝra dǝben sǝron futǝ PPE a OSHA shawori kasuwa fufuben sadǝna ta'adir tǝwal kafa arakǝbe lamkate jama kasuwa SARS-CoV-2 zamzǝna au tǝmatǝna dǝga Ferno Aerosal bǝ dga kǝngalan.
Larda United States, a NIOSH- tawadǝ N95 fufu a sasǝrtǝ au nzǝlifo kamilla fufuro kǝnjoro fasal adǝbe sǝronzǝn jaraftǝga, alamma kuru jarawi laitabe a samma mbeji..
Sǝro fasalla kafsǝnabedǝn tartiffa ngalau kǝnga cidawubega ngalutǝbye mbeji. Huwwuma Nalewa Dunyabe WHO shawori kamilla cǝnyi kǝla kasuwa a COVID-19 dǝ kasuwa fufuben illa kasuwa adǝga kamro faltǝyin zǝnggu tiyemen.
Huwuma WHO shawori tok tilo cinadǝ shima zambu gaworam nji kam retǝben tǝdindǝma.
Kuru sandi donyi launo kasuwa fufube gotǝnamadǝga saftǝga sandi kasuwa COVID-19 sǝdanadǝga kza sadin madǝ ferno aerosol be madǝ shim Huwuma WHO cǝ futǝ zambu fuskabe liatabe a gafsǝna zǝga faidatǝwo.
Fasal aerosolle ladǝn zambu litabedǝ shima fasal N95 be au FFP2 be fufube dǝga faljin.
Awo adadu PPE bero danadǝ Dunya samma sǝtin bawo, adǝbe sǝkǝ huwuma WHO shawori cinadǝ muradǝ kalambo PPE dǝga diwal telemedicinena nǝmgade zahir begadǝn faltǝ alamanna kasamram ngǝla a kur sandi donyi njim kam COVID 19 sǝdanabero ganamen, kuru shi PPE dǝ mburo waljiya do shilan faidatǝ tiyi fufubedǝn tǝluwo baro loktǝ rewi am dondi kadabe gattǝbeln.
