b'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) dǝ shi dǝ enzyme dǝwo kadiyi diya ye (cell membranes) cells ye dǝro kǝrrata suro futu, cawu, katǝgǝ, kǝndǝliram, kalǝm-a so ye lan.
ACE2 dǝ cidawa angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) gade so ye dǝga angǝsshin adadu angiotensin-II ye dǝga fulutǝ men kuru Ang (1-7) dǝga yira men shiya kurun dunowa kwasa katǝgǝ ye kuruntǝye sǝdin. ACE2 so dǝye alama nabtǝ garam koronabairos la do ye suro cells ye ro yeyin kara.
Jili enzyme dǝ ye adamngana ye nzǝ dǝ sha hACE2 lan buwotin.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 dǝ shi dǝ zinc suronzǝn metalloenzyme sami endothelial -a cells gade-a so yen.
ACE2 protein dǝ suronzǝn N-terminal peptidase M2 domain -a kuru C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain -a mbeji.
ACE2 dǝ shi single-pass type I membrane protein, enzymatically active domain nzǝ dǝ sami cell dǝye ro ro kata suro fufu-a kǝndǝwuwa gade-a yen.
Extracellular domain ACE2 ye dǝ transmembrane domain dǝn zakkata enzyme la gade sheddase lan nowata ye, kuru protein fata dǝ suro buye dǝro fitǝyin kuru chollo ro waltǝ fitǝyin.
ACE2 dǝ suro kǝnduwuwa nguwu yen mbeji: ACE2 dǝ tiyi cell membrane mainly lung type II alveolar cells ye dǝro kǝrrata enterocytes small intestine ye ro, arterial -a venous endothelial cells -a arterial smooth muscle cells suro kǝnduwuwa nguwu yen.
ACE2 mRNA ye bayantǝ nzǝ ye suro cerebral cortex, striatum, hypothalamus, brainstem -a yen tuwondǝna.
Cida buroye ACE2 ye dǝ shima ACE dǝga kalkaltǝgǝ.
ACE dǝ cleaves angiotensin I hormone dǝga kamzǝ vasoconstricting angiotensin II ro kalakcin.
ACE2 dǝ ye waltǝ carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine kamjin angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuru hydrolyses it into the vasodilator angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 draksǝ adadu peptides ye dǝga kamjin suro dǝn [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, and ghrelin mbeji.
ACE2 dǝ kuruman also regulates the membrane trafficking neutral amino acid transporter ye dǝga kalkalzǝyin SLC6A19 kuru suro kwasa Hartnup ye dǝn kǝrawzǝna.
nabtǝ transmembrane protein yeyi lan, ACE2 dǝ alama nabtǝ garam kura koronabairos la so yeyin karauro dǝn HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (kuli kwasabe dǝwo SARS suwudin dǝ); kuru SARS-CoV-2 (kuli kwasabe dǝwo COVID-19 suwudin ma).
Musamman ma so, spike S1 protein SARS-CoV dǝ kǝltǝnzǝ dǝ-a SARS-CoV2 ye dǝ-a enzymatic domain ACE2 dǝga kǝla on the surface cells yen endocytosis -a translocation kuli kwasabe dǝga suwudin of both kuli kwasabe dǝga enzyme ye dǝga endosomes suro ma dǝ.
Garam adǝ mǝradǝ s priming of the S protein by the host serine protease TMPRSS2, awo shiro takal suwudin so dǝye kwamison kǝla kulashi yen kara nabtǝ kurun yen. Adǝ ye nazaru la suwudǝ gǝnazǝgǝna kǝla adadu ACE2 ye dǝ fulutǝ dǝ, suro cells ye dǝn, kwasa kǝriwtǝ ro banajin.
Adǝyeyi ma, karabkawa ilmuwuye kada shawari kǝla ACE inhibitor -a kurun ARB ye-a faidatǝ yen.
Fasal la nazaruye-a meta-analysis ye-a yim July 11, 2012 lǝbtǝna dǝ ye, fǝlezǝna kǝla "ACE inhibitors lan faidatǝ dǝ kashi 34% lan tajirwa kwasa namusu yen fulutǝna fǝlezǝna."
Ngawo adǝyen, "tajirwa kwasa namusu ye dǝ fulutǝna am dǝwo sandiya ACE inhibitors lan kurun tǝdǝna so dǝn sandi dǝwo zauro tajirwa kwasa namusu ye ma so dǝn, musamman ma ro am dǝwo kwasa kaltǝgǝye so dǝn.
ACE inhibitors lan faidatǝ dǝ kǝrmu kwasa namusu ye fulutǝ dǝro leyata, son yayi natija dǝ ngǝlaro kǝzǝbkǝ gǝnyi tajirwa kwasa namusu ye dǝn yeyi ro.
Recombinant human ACE2 (rhACE2) dǝ sha kasartǝn kurun bǝlin kwasa kǝraw fufuye ye ro, kuru alama pulmonary hemodynamics -a oxygen saturation suro piglets with a lipopolysaccharide-induced acute respiratory distress syndrome so dǝga ngalawzoyin ro.
Ro reta- reta rhACE2 ye suro adamngana ye dǝ alama awa 10 yeyi kuru cida baditǝnzǝn dǝ alama minti 30 yeyi kǝla loktǝ gǝrtǝye (loktu) awa 24 yen.
Kulashi kada ye fǝlezǝna kǝla rhACE2 dǝ kurun ngǝlama ro waljin am dǝwo classic renin-angiotensin system inhibitors ye wazǝna so dǝro (RAS inhibitors) aw kwasa dǝwo ne letǝ angiotensin II ye dǝ habtǝna so ye dǝn. is Infused rhACE2 dǝ jarabtǝna liyitarin kurun kwasa yintǝye zauro kǝraw ma ro.
b'COVID-19 APP so fasal la talfon muskoye sha kam letǝgǝna so baranǝm gotǝro dawarratǝ suro bana wawa koronabairos ye 2019-20 ye dǝn, adǝ shima fasal dǝwo kam asutaye ("am letana ma so") dǝwo kam zamtǝna ro letana so do.
Application kada nyatǝn bana gomnatiye men bǝlawa la so dǝn.
Nzunduwa kada apps kam baranǝm gotǝye tǝnandǝna.
Shiwalla ashir faitǝye kada manatǝna, musamman ma ro kǝla fasal dǝwo ne ba kam apps dǝ faidatin ye fǝlejin so ye dǝn.
Fasal la gade kaykay butuwa su suro dǝn bluetooth men faidatǝ nǝm karǝngǝ faidatǝma dǝye talfonwa gadeya ye so.
Yim 10 April 2020, Google-a Apple-a ye citilowa ro mawuzana kǝla fasal la bluetooth apps ye dawu Android-a iOS-a ye ro sakin sana.
China lan, gomnati dǝ kǝlakǝl Alipay ye men, apps la sawudǝna shi dǝwo am lardǝye kolzǝ kam COVID-19 ro letana wa kulassan nozain ma ye.
Bǝrniwa China ye 200 samin yin gaodatayin. Singapore lan, apps la shiro an app called "TraceTogether" sayin dǝn faidatayin.
App dǝ am la bǝlaye lamar IT ye ma so satande, sha ndu soye faidatin ro kollata, kuru sha gomnati ro jatǝyin. North Macedonia ye "StopKorona!" Kǝrtǝ ro sǝkǝna, app la bluetooth ye kam zamtǝna ro tǝtǝg kulasta ye kuru duwaro nǝlefa ro cistuwu so ro bayanna cin ma.
App dǝ Ministry of Communication and Technology -a and Ministry of Health -a satande.
Yim 14 April 2020, app amar kǝnjo gǝrejin na Google Play Store -a Apple App Store -a yen.
Yim 12 April, gomnati ye mawuzǝna kǝla app kam kulasnǝm gotǝye dǝ tandonzǝ dǝ cintuzǝna yen, kuru man suro mawu gana yen tuwondin ro waljin. App jili dǝye Ireland yin nyatǝna, France yen ("StopCovid").
Australia -a New Zealand -a so Singapore's TraceTogether app dǝga wuzayin BlueTrace protocol la. Russia ye geofencing app kudo nyazǝna am COVID-19 i zamzǝna suro Moscow yen dasawuna so ro, dawarratǝ wande fanza kolzanyi ro tawattǝgǝ ro.
Ross Anderson, professor of security engineering at Cambridge University ye dǝye, kaziyiyya la isabsǝna kǝla fasal app ye dǝn, suro dǝn jire gnyi fǝletǝ so kuru man nǝm ngalaw ba so buro man am gana lan baditiya.
Kǝla kaziyiyya app illa ma so tartǝgǝ yen manajin,"coronavirus" apps, so, Apple ye kalangay sǝkǝna kǝla karabka jiliwi so raksa app koronabairos ye dǝ suwondayin yen suro App Store nzǝ ye dǝn, kal sǝkǝ illa "maila" aw karabka la suwa suwunnǝm la gǝnyi ma ro cido.
Google kuru Amazon ye kal jili adǝ sǝkǝna.
Am kǝla hakku ashir faitǝye yen mana ma so ye kuttu nza manazana kǝla ashir jama ye kuru tǝdin app koronabairos so ye dǝ men yen, musamman ma ro awowa ashir kuruye koronabairos nankaro tǝdǝna so sa wawa dǝ kamzǝ kojiya fuktǝ wartin wa ro.
Amnesty International -a kuru karabkawa gade 100 samin kawuli la sotoluwuna kǝla ashir kuru jili adǝ fulutǝ yen.
Karabkawa dǝye shartǝwa wusku kǝla cidawa gomnati yen mawuzana:
Ashir kuru dǝ "halal, mbu, kuru sandǝna" ro walzǝ;
Shim yiko-a ashir kuru-a dǝ furo gǝrtǝyin ma loktǝnzǝ datǝ ye dǝga fete ro bayantǝ;
Bayanna dǝn faidatǝ dǝ kǝla COVID-19 ye bas lan dazǝ;
Nzǝrifo bayanna ye-a su gǝratǝ-a dǝ tǝliona ro walzǝ kuru shada tǝliona dǝ ye fǝletǝ;
Ashir kuru digital ye dǝ lamar dǝ ro konnu futuwi ro katǝ kuru ngayitǝ so ranna son katǝna ro walzǝ.
Bayanna kam gade kǝn yakkǝ me ro yo dǝ sharaye kasatsǝna ro walzǝ;
Njodkunotǝ son faitǝ-a hakku jamaye kǝla njodkuno yen manatǝ-a mbeji ro walzǝ;
"gǝntǝgǝ faida ma" nduwa nduwana soye "gawilwu saniya wuzǝna ma"so ye mǝradǝtin, suro dǝn gonyiwa lamar nǝlefa jamaye so-a am dǝwo rangata so-a mbeji. German Chaos Computer Club (CCC) -a Reporters Without Borders (Reporter ohne Grenzen) (RSF) -a ye suwa la satoluwuna.
Dawari dǝwo Google/Apple -a ye nyatǝna dǝ nyanzan kaziyi ashir dawartin ba ro kuriye dǝ ba ro diwo awo dǝwo ashir zayin dǝga suro operating system device nza ye dǝn fittǝ men.
Lardǝwa la so dǝ ye na kam dǝgana kuru network ye men faidatayin sudu app ye dǝro, mǝradǝ app saye-a nyiya kurun katǝ-a ba ro cido.
Israel lan ashir kuru jili network ye ma dǝ amartǝgǝna.
Nzunduwa network lan faidatin so dǝwo bayanna naye suwondǝ surin ma sodǝ kaziyi ashir faitǝye zauro mbeji.
Adǝyeyi ma, fasal dǝwo Central server woso gǝnyi bayyana na dlgamaye nojin; kaidawa bayanna faitǝye kada tǝdǝna sandi dǝwo Central server lan faidatayin so dǝ intercommunication ro bas faidatin (ma cidaye dǝn ruyi).
South Korea lan, fasal la app ye gǝnyi ma lan faidatǝ am letana so dǝ matǝ gotǝna.
Sudu app la musamman yen faidatǝ ye dǝro, fasal dǝ ye bayanna maa kada lan sabsǝ suro dǝn talfon so, kati kawo tuloye so, anyi kǝlza tuskaza.
Bayanna adǝ faidata am letana so ro watiya zuwatye ngawon, gomnati ye kuru man bayanna ba dǝye dǝ jama ro tarzǝna, adǝ amarratǝ sawo wawa MERSye ro.
Bayanna adǝ raksa jamaye suwondayin apps kada website men. Lardǝwa alama Germany sodǝn zawalwa ndi son faidatǝ.
Yim 6 April 2020 lan, bayanna kǝzǝbkǝ ro ba.
Ashir- am letana ye manǝm gotǝ dǝ shawari ngǝla, kulashi kada kǝla dǝn tǝdǝna tǝn 2013 lan. Kəntagə Aprilbe kaunzə 7 saa 2020 lan, jami goiwabe dozəm falma kozəna kəla diwal ashirtəgə-ro kəji mataben cidazayin, misal ro "Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE)" faidatəm kam faidatəmabe nəm karungunzə sha waya gade'a ro gawo ro.
Adəgaima, PEPP-PT də fasal kəla kəlye do suronzən katappa na fallo saptəgə-a kuru tartə-abe indi so mbeji ma, kuru shi də ka'ida tilo gənyi. Ka'idawa na fallo saptəgənyi ye dawu lan "Decentralized Privacy-Preserving Proximity Tracing (DP-PPT/DP-ǝT)" so, "Temporary Contact Numbers (TCN, fka Contact Event Numbers, CEN)" so, "Privacy Sensitive Protocols and Mechanisms for Mobile Contact Tracing (PACT)" kuru gade gabsəna so'a samma mbeji
Ka'idawa anyi lan, sapsawi bayannabe ngəmbe asutinma so də təmma ro awo faidatəbe (misal ro waya) koljimba, kuru kalkaltə samma so kəla awo shima dəyen wakajin.
Jami naptə kəlanzəbe "MIT Media Lab"be də awo shiro "SafePaths" sayin də tando sədin, adə shiye ngərwo nzunduwa ashirtəgə-liobe ro faidatin sa sapsawi bayanbe kəla na au zawal gurotəgə kəla tartəgə COVID-19ben baratin maa.
Adəye kulashi 'whitepaper'be shiro "Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic" sayin do kənagə Marchbe saa 2020 lan tutuluwuna də ro tənga'atəgə. Ngənəwu gade adəga samun də shi ma "SafeTrace platform by Enigma MPC" , kamfani do nzunduwa ashirtəgəbe sətandin ma do buro salakyen "MIT Media Lab" sha koksəna ma də.
"SafeTrace" də nzunduwa 'hardware'be nzəliwo'a faidatin faidatəwu'a kolzə sapsawi bayanbe ashirre kəla na be-a nəlewabe-a am faidatəwu gade so-a ndi katenzan faidatayin, ashirtəgə sapsawi bayanbe də bannazayimba ro.
Kəntagə Aprilbe kaunzə 5 saa 2020, "the global TCN Coalition" də jamiwa kəlanza kəlzanaye kokkada, awo nganzazana shima nəm gadetə fulutə-akuru duya samma son cidatə appwa kam baratəbe hangal gərtəgəbe-aye, lamar kura fal gota tarrataa fandobe.
Kəntagə Aprilbe kaunzə 9 saa 2020 lan, gumnati Singaporebe awo shiro "the BlueTrace protocol" sayin do "official government app" nzəye faidatin ma də ndu soye raksə sowandin ro sədəna sə warmajio.
Kəntagə Aprilbe kaunzə 10 saa 2020be lan, Google-a Apple-a, kamfaniwa do ngərwowa Androidbe-a iOSbe-a sonotin də, cida amma manəm fandobe baditə warma'ada, shi doni gultəzan ashirtə səliwin, "Bluetooth Low Energy technology"-a "privacy-preserving cryptography" kəltə men.
Sandiye kuru ka'idawa nzunduwa zamanbe gədima suro nzundu au fasal dəyen faidatin ma də baksana.
Gultə Apple-a Google-a yen, fasal shima də katappa yakkə lan zunəm tulo nyiyatə:
karewa cidabe tulo do gomnati'a banazə manhaj koronabairos baranəm fandobe do ashirtə-siliwin sətandin.
Raktə cida adə diobe də iOS-a Android-a ro ikko: Google-a Apple-aye dawari sadin kazəyi citəbe-a lamarra ro shim ikkobe-a ro katap gotəgəro buro salakyen fasal də "operating system updates" men samtə men, kuru dare futu buron təkkəna yedei lan tulo sa kuwa də ba ro waljiya.
Kurun ba gaden gǝnatǝ (shi doni faida kurunne waltǝm faltǝ, au faidawanzǝ yira lan notǝna dǝ) shima kurun laa kasatkata kwasa gade ro au nǝm dondi laa gade do shi nankaro gǝnyi sha tǝnandǝna ro faidatǝ.
Adǝ lai kulashi ilmube fal do kǝrmaaro tǝgana kurun COVID-19be nǝlewa-aye kuru faidajinye tando nankaro.
Diwalla kulashibe gade ye suro lan kalimi COVID-19be tando-a kuru "convalescent plasma transfusion". SARS-CoV-2 protinwanzǝ 66 yedei kurun tǝdin ma mbeji nda so wo so na shiro kǝrtǝyin tiyinzǝn kada mbeji.
Na'a kəltabe anyi kulastə də cida ma'ana-a kurun kuli kwasa COVID-19be "protein" wanzəbe ro kurun matabe cin?
Protein SARS-CoV-2 be taratin maye suronzan "papain-like protease, RNA dependent RNA polymerase, helicase, S protein, kuru ADP ribophosphatase" mbeji.
